WEBVTT

00:00:06.332 --> 00:00:08.764
 "THE FOLLOWING"
 "SPECIAL ENCORE PRESENTATION"

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:11.400
 "OF THE KENNEDY CENTER TONIGHT"
 "PRODUCTION OF MEDEA"

00:00:11.432 --> 00:00:15.432
 "IS MADE POSSIBLE BY THE"
 "SUPPORT OF VIEWERS LIKE YOU."

00:01:38.064 --> 00:01:40.864
 "I WISH THE LONG SHIP"
 "ARGO HAD NEVER PASSED"

00:01:40.900 --> 00:01:45.832
 "THAT PERILOUS CHANNEL"
 "BETWEEN THE SYMPLEGADES."

00:01:45.864 --> 00:01:49.332
 "I WISH THE PINES THAT MADE"
 "HER MAST AND HER OARS"

00:01:49.364 --> 00:01:53.100
 "STILL WAVED IN THE WIND ON MOUNT"
 "PELION, AND THE GRAY FISHHAWK"

00:01:53.132 --> 00:01:57.732
 "STILL NESTED IN THEM, THE GREAT"
 "ADVENTURERS HAD NEVER VOYAGED"

00:01:57.764 --> 00:02:01.000
 "INTO THE ASIAN SUNRISE"
 "TO THE SHORES OF MORNING"

00:02:01.032 --> 00:02:04.000
 "FOR THE"
 "GOLDEN FLEECE."

00:02:04.032 --> 00:02:09.300
 "FOR THEN MY MISTRESS MEDEA"
 "WOULD NEVER HAVE SEEN JASON"

00:02:09.332 --> 00:02:13.432
 "NOR LOVED AND SAVED HIM,"
 "NOR CUT HERSELF OFF FROM HOME"

00:02:13.464 --> 00:02:16.032
 "TO COME WITH HIM INTO THIS"
 "COUNTRY OF THE SMILING"

00:02:16.064 --> 00:02:20.064
 "CHATTERING GREEKS AND"
 "THE ROOFS OF CORINTH:"

00:02:20.100 --> 00:02:27.164
 "OVER WHICH I SEE EVIL"
 "HANG LIKE A CLOUD."

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:32.564
 "FOR SHE IS NOT MEEK BUT FIERCE,"
 "AND THE DAUGHTER OF A KING."

00:02:32.600 --> 00:02:36.764
 "YET AT FIRST"
 "ALL WENT WELL."

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:39.032
 "THE FOLK OF CORINTH"
 "WERE KIND TO HER,"

00:02:39.064 --> 00:02:43.264
 "THEY WERE PROUD OF HER"
 "BEAUTY, AND JASON LOVED HER."

00:02:43.300 --> 00:02:46.200
 "HAPPY IS THE HOUSE WHERE"
 "THE MAN AND THE WOMAN LOVE"

00:02:46.232 --> 00:02:49.764
 "AND ARE FAITHFUL."

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:56.064
 "NOW ALL IS CHANGED;"
 "ALL IS BLACK HATRED."

00:02:56.100 --> 00:02:59.300
 "FOR JASON HAS TURNED FROM"
 "HER; HE CALLS THE OLD BOND"

00:02:59.332 --> 00:03:03.900
 "A BARBARIAN MATING, NOT A GREEK"
 "MARRIAGE; HE HAS CAST HER OFF"

00:03:03.932 --> 00:03:07.332
 "AND WEDDED THE YELLOW-HAIRED"
 "CHILD OF CREON, THE RULER HERE."

00:03:07.364 --> 00:03:09.764
 "HE WANTS WORLDLY"
 "ADVANTAGE, FINE FRIENDS,"

00:03:09.800 --> 00:03:12.132
 "AND A HIGH"
 "PLACE IN CORINTH"

00:03:12.164 --> 00:03:15.864
 "AND FOR THESE HE IS WILLING"
 "TO CAST MEDEA LIKE A HARLOT,"

00:03:15.900 --> 00:03:19.732
 "AND BETRAY THE CHILDREN"
 "THAT SHE HAS BORNE HIM."

00:03:19.764 --> 00:03:23.132
 "HE IS NOT WISE, I THINK."

00:03:23.164 --> 00:03:29.264
 "BUT MEDEA LIES IN THE HOUSE,"
 "BROKEN WITH PAIN AND RAGE,"

00:03:29.300 --> 00:03:34.000
 "SHE WILL NEITHER EAT NOR"
 "DRINK, EXCEPT HER OWN TEARS."

00:03:34.032 --> 00:03:37.100
 "SHE TURNS HER FACE TOWARD"
 "THE EARTH, REMEMBERING HER"

00:03:37.132 --> 00:03:40.164
 "FATHER'S HOUSE AND HER NATIVE"
 "LAND WHICH SHE ABANDONED"

00:03:40.200 --> 00:03:44.032
 "FOR LOVE OF THIS MAN"
 "WHO NOW DESPISES HER."

00:03:44.064 --> 00:03:48.032
 "AND IF I TRY TO SPEAK COMFORT"
 "TO HER SHE ONLY STARES AT ME,"

00:03:48.064 --> 00:03:52.300
 "GREAT EYES LIKE STONES."

00:03:52.332 --> 00:03:56.164
 "SHE IS LIKE A STONE ON THE"
 "SHORE OR A WAVE OF THE SEA,"

00:03:56.200 --> 00:04:01.332
 "AND I THINK SHE HATES"
 "EVEN HER CHILDREN."

00:04:01.364 --> 00:04:04.300
 "SHE'S LEARNING WHAT"
 "IT IS TO BE A FOREIGNER,"

00:04:04.332 --> 00:04:07.264
 "CAST OUT, ALONE"
 "AND DESPISED."

00:04:07.300 --> 00:04:09.832
 "SHE WILL NEVER LEARN TO BE"
 "HUMBLE, SHE WILL NEVER LEARN"

00:04:09.864 --> 00:04:12.364
 "TO DRINK INSULT LIKE"
 "HARMLESS WATER."

00:04:12.400 --> 00:04:15.100
 "OH, I'M IN TERROR OF HER;"
 "WHETHER SHE'LL THREAD A KNIFE"

00:04:15.132 --> 00:04:17.600
 "THROUGH HER OWN HEART,"
 "OR WHETHER SHE'LL HUNT THE"

00:04:17.632 --> 00:04:20.100
 "BRIDEGROOM AND HIS NEW BRIDE,"
 "OR WHAT MORE DREADFUL EVIL"

00:04:20.132 --> 00:04:23.600
 "STALKS THROUGH THE"
 "FOREST OF HER DARK MIND."

00:04:23.632 --> 00:04:26.932
 "I KNOW THAT JASON WOULD HAVE"
 "BEEN WISER TO TEMPT A LIONESS,"

00:04:26.964 --> 00:04:31.332
 "OR NAKED-HANDED STEAL"
 "THE WHELPS OF A TIGER."

00:04:31.364 --> 00:04:33.264
 "HERE COME THE"
 "HAPPY CHILDREN."

00:04:33.300 --> 00:04:36.332
 "LITTLE THEY KNOW OF"
 "THEIR MOTHER'S GRIEF."

00:04:45.632 --> 00:04:47.532
 "IS SHE STILL IN THAT"
 "DEEP DESPAIR?"

00:04:47.564 --> 00:04:50.864
 "YOU ARE LUCKY, OLD"
 "WATCHDOG OF JASON'S BOYS,"

00:04:50.900 --> 00:04:52.764
 "YOU DO NOT"
 "SEE HER."

00:04:52.800 --> 00:04:55.464
 "THIS EVIL IS NOT DECLINING,"
 "IT IS JUST AT DAWN."

00:04:55.500 --> 00:04:58.132
 "I DREAD THE LION-EYED"
 "GLARE OF ITS NOON."

00:04:58.164 --> 00:05:00.364
 "IS SHE SO WROUGHT?"

00:05:00.400 --> 00:05:03.432
 "YET NEITHER YOU NOR MEDEA"
 "KNOWS THE LATEST AND WORST."

00:05:03.464 --> 00:05:04.964
 "WHAT? WHAT?"

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:07.700
 "I SHOULDN'T"
 "HAVE SPOKEN."

00:05:07.732 --> 00:05:10.900
 "YOU AND I ARE TWO SLAVES,"
 "WE CAN TRUST EACH OTHER,"

00:05:10.932 --> 00:05:13.800
 "I HEARD THEM SAYING, WHEN WE"
 "WALKED BESIDE THE HOLY FOUNTAIN"

00:05:13.832 --> 00:05:18.100
 "PEIRENE WHERE THE OLD MEN SIT IN"
 "THE SUN ON THE STONE BENCHES,"

00:05:18.132 --> 00:05:21.864
 "THEY WERE SAYING THAT CREON, THE"
 "LORD OF THIS LAND, INTENDS TO"

00:05:21.900 --> 00:05:26.132
 "DRIVE OUT MEDEA AND THE CHILDREN"
 "WITH HER, THESE INNOCENT BOYS,"

00:05:26.164 --> 00:05:28.900
 "OUT OF THIS HOUSE AND OUT OF"
 "CORINTH, AND THEY MUST WANDER"

00:05:28.932 --> 00:05:31.664
 "THE WILD WORLD"
 "HOMELESS AND HELPLESS."

00:05:31.700 --> 00:05:34.800
 "I DON'T BELIEVE IT. NO,"
 "JASON MAY HATE THE MOTHER"

00:05:34.832 --> 00:05:38.600
 "BUT HE WOULD HARDLY"
 "LET HIS SONS BE CAST OUT."

00:05:38.632 --> 00:05:40.464
 "LISTEN: I HEAR"
 "HER VOICE."

00:05:40.500 --> 00:05:43.664
 "TAKE THE CHILDREN AWAY,"
 "KEEP THEM AWAY FROM HER."

00:05:43.700 --> 00:05:47.100
 "TAKE THEM TO THE"
 "OTHER DOOR. QUICKLY."

00:05:52.464 --> 00:05:55.064
 "DEATH IS MY WISH..."

00:05:55.100 --> 00:05:58.900
 "FOR MYSELF, MY"
 "ENEMIES, MY CHILDREN."

00:05:58.932 --> 00:06:01.432
 "THIS IS MY TERROR: TO HEAR"
 "HER ALWAYS HARKING BACK"

00:06:01.464 --> 00:06:04.064
 "TO THE CHILDREN, LIKE A"
 "FIERCE HOUND AT FAULT."

00:06:04.100 --> 00:06:07.700
 "OH, UNHAPPY ONE,"
 "THEY'RE NOT TO BLAME."

00:06:07.732 --> 00:06:12.664
 "IF ANY GOD HEARS ME:"
 "LET ME DIE."

00:06:12.700 --> 00:06:16.300
 "OH, IT'S A BAD THING TO BE BORN"
 "OF HIGH RACE AND BROUGHT UP"

00:06:16.332 --> 00:06:20.332
 "WILLFUL AND POWERFUL IN A GREAT"
 "HOUSE, UNRULED AND RULING MANY:"

00:06:20.364 --> 00:06:23.432
 "FOR THEN IF MISFORTUNE"
 "COMES IT IS UNENDURABLE,"

00:06:23.464 --> 00:06:27.164
 "I SAY THAT POOR PEOPLE ARE"
 "HAPPIER: LITTLE COMMONERS"

00:06:27.200 --> 00:06:30.500
 "AND HUMBLE PEOPLE, THE POOR IN"
 "SPIRIT: THEY CAN LIE LOW UNDER"

00:06:30.532 --> 00:06:33.432
 "THE WIND AND LIVE: WHILE THE"
 "TALL OAKS AND CLOUD-RAKING"

00:06:33.464 --> 00:06:39.200
 "MOUNTAIN PINES GO MAD IN THE"
 "STORM, WRITHE, GROAN AND CRASH."

00:06:39.232 --> 00:06:43.464
 "THIS IS THE WILD AND"
 "TERRIBLE JUSTICE OF GOD:"

00:06:43.500 --> 00:06:50.032
 "IT BRINGS ON GREAT PERSONS"
 "THE GREAT DISASTERS."

00:06:50.064 --> 00:06:52.164
 "WHAT DO YOU WANT?"

00:06:52.200 --> 00:06:56.100
 "I HEAR HER CRYING AGAIN:"
 "IT IS DREADFUL."

00:06:56.132 --> 00:06:57.664
 "HER LAMENTATION."

00:06:57.700 --> 00:07:01.432
 "SHE IS BEAUTIFUL AND DEEP IN"
 "GRIEF: WE COULDN'T HELP COMING."

00:07:01.464 --> 00:07:04.664
 "WE ARE FRIENDS OF THIS HOUSE"
 "AND ITS TROUBLE HURTS US."

00:07:04.700 --> 00:07:10.400
 "YOU ARE RIGHT, FRIENDS,"
 "IT'S NOT A HOME. IT'S BROKEN."

00:07:10.432 --> 00:07:15.900
 "OLD AND HONORED SERVANT OF A"
 "GREAT HOUSE: DO YOU THINK IT IS"

00:07:15.932 --> 00:07:18.800
 "WISE TO LEAVE YOUR"
 "LADY ALONE IN THERE,"

00:07:18.832 --> 00:07:22.600
 "BUILDING THAT TERRIBLE"
 "ACROPOLIS OF DEADLY THOUGHTS?"

00:07:22.632 --> 00:07:27.200
 "WE GREEKS BELIEVE THAT"
 "SOLITUDE IS VERY DANGEROUS,"

00:07:27.232 --> 00:07:30.732
 "GREAT PASSIONS GROW INTO"
 "MONSTERS IN THE DARK"

00:07:30.764 --> 00:07:35.832
 "OF THE MIND; BUT IF YOU SHARE"
 "THEM WITH LOVING FRIENDS"

00:07:35.864 --> 00:07:41.864
 "THEY REMAIN HUMAN,"
 "THEY CAN BE ENDURED."

00:07:41.900 --> 00:07:45.432
 "SHE HAS LIVED AMONG US,"
 "WE'VE LEARNED TO LOVE HER,"

00:07:45.464 --> 00:07:47.864
 "WE'D GLADLY"
 "TELL HER SO."

00:07:47.900 --> 00:07:51.964
 "IT MIGHT COMFORT"
 "HER SPIRIT."

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:54.300
 "DO YOU THINK SO?"

00:07:54.332 --> 00:07:57.500
 "SHE WOULDN'T LISTEN."

00:07:57.532 --> 00:07:59.432
 "OH, SHE IS COMING!"

00:07:59.464 --> 00:08:05.964
 "SPEAK CAREFULLY TO HER; MAKE"
 "YOUR WORDS A SOFT MUSIC."

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:11.764
 "OH MY DEAR,"
 "MY POOR CHILD."

00:08:11.800 --> 00:08:15.664
 "THEY SAY SHE"
 "IS DANGEROUS."

00:08:15.700 --> 00:08:18.864
 "LOOK AT HER EYES."

00:08:18.900 --> 00:08:23.764
 "SHE IS A WITCH,"
 "BUT NOT EVIL."

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:28.032
 "SHE CAN MAKE OLD"
 "MEN YOUNG AGAIN:"

00:08:28.064 --> 00:08:32.200
 "ALL THE PEOPLE OF HER"
 "COUNTRY ARE WITCHES."

00:08:32.232 --> 00:08:34.664
 "THEY KNOW ABOUT"
 "DRUGS AND MAGIC."

00:08:34.700 --> 00:08:41.164
 "THEY ARE SAVAGES, BUT"
 "THEY HAVE A WILD WISDOM."

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:46.100
 "I WILL LOOK AT THE LIGHT"
 "OF THE SUN, THIS LAST TIME."

00:08:46.132 --> 00:08:49.432
 "I WISH FROM THAT BLUE SKY"
 "THE WHITE WOLF OF LIGHTNING"

00:08:49.464 --> 00:08:52.964
 "WOULD LEAP, AND BURST"
 "MY SKULL AND MY BRAIN,"

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:58.964
 "AND LIKE A BURNING BABE"
 "CLING TO THESE BREASTS."

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:01.732
 "SOMEONE IS HERE?"

00:09:01.764 --> 00:09:05.432
 "I DID NOT KNOW"
 "I HAD VISITORS."

00:09:05.464 --> 00:09:11.132
 "WOMEN OF CORINTH: IF ANYTHING"
 "HAS BEEN SPOKEN TOO LOUDLY HERE,"

00:09:11.164 --> 00:09:13.432
 "CONSIDER THAT I"
 "BELIEVED I WAS ALONE;"

00:09:13.464 --> 00:09:16.164
 "AND I HAVE"
 "SOME PROVOCATION."

00:09:16.200 --> 00:09:18.932
 "YOU'VE COME, LET ME SUPPOSE,"
 "WITH LOVE AND SYMPATHY "

00:09:18.964 --> 00:09:21.500
 "TO PEER AT MY SORROW."

00:09:21.532 --> 00:09:24.064
 "I UNDERSTAND WELL ENOUGH"
 "THAT NOTHING IS EVER PRIVATE"

00:09:24.100 --> 00:09:26.600
 "IN A GREEK CITY; WHOEVER"
 "WITHHOLDS ANYTHING"

00:09:26.632 --> 00:09:28.900
 "IS THOUGHT"
 "SULLEN OR PROUD."

00:09:28.932 --> 00:09:31.864
 "UNDEMOCRATIC I"
 "THINK YOU CALL IT."

00:09:31.900 --> 00:09:35.200
 "THIS IS NOT ALWAYS JUST,"
 "BUT WE KNOW THAT JUSTICE,"

00:09:35.232 --> 00:09:39.732
 "AT LEAST ON EARTH,"
 "IS A NAME, NOT A FACT."

00:09:39.764 --> 00:09:47.964
 "AND AS FOR ME, I WISH TO AVOID"
 "ANY APPEARANCE OF BEING PROUD."

00:09:48.000 --> 00:09:53.264
 "OF WHAT? OF"
 "AFFLICTION?"

00:09:53.300 --> 00:09:56.700
 "I WILL SHOW YOU"
 "MY NAKED HEART."

00:09:56.732 --> 00:10:00.132
 "YOU KNOW THAT MY LORD JASON"
 "HAS LEFT ME AND MADE A SECOND"

00:10:00.164 --> 00:10:02.900
 "MARRIAGE WITH THE BRIGHT-HAIRED"
 "CHILD OF WEALTH AND POWER."

00:10:02.932 --> 00:10:06.232
 "I TOO WAS A CHILD OF POWER,"
 "BUT NOT IN THIS COUNTRY;"

00:10:06.264 --> 00:10:09.232
 "AND I SPENT MY POWER"
 "FOR LOVE OF JASON."

00:10:09.264 --> 00:10:11.732
 "I POURED IT OUT"
 "BEFORE HIM LIKE WATER,"

00:10:11.764 --> 00:10:13.800
 "I MADE HIM DRINK"
 "IT LIKE WINE."

00:10:13.832 --> 00:10:17.564
 "I GAVE HIM SUCCESS AND FAME;"
 "I SAVED HIM HIS PRECIOUS LIFE;"

00:10:17.600 --> 00:10:19.732
 "NOT ONCE, MANY TIMES."

00:10:19.764 --> 00:10:22.564
 "YOU MAY HAVE HEARD"
 "WHAT I DID FOR HIM:"

00:10:22.600 --> 00:10:28.564
 "I BETRAYED MY FATHER FOR HIM, I"
 "KILLED MY BROTHER TO SAVE HIM;"

00:10:28.600 --> 00:10:32.964
 "I MADE MY OWN LAND"
 "TO HATE ME FOREVER;"

00:10:33.000 --> 00:10:37.100
 "AND I FLED WEST WITH"
 "JASON IN THE GREEK SHIP,"

00:10:37.132 --> 00:10:41.000
 "UNDER THE THUNDER OF "
 "SAIL, WEEPING AND LAUGHING,"

00:10:41.032 --> 00:10:44.200
 "THAT HUGE JOURNEY"
 "THROUGH THE BLACK SEA"

00:10:44.232 --> 00:10:46.632
 "AND THE BOSPHORUS, WHERE"
 "THE ROCKS CLANG TOGETHER,"

00:10:46.664 --> 00:10:49.800
 "THROUGH THE SEA OF MARMORA,"
 "AND THROUGH THE HELLESPONT,"

00:10:49.832 --> 00:10:53.764
 "WATCHED BY THE SPEARMEN"
 "OF WEALTHY TROY, AND HOME"

00:10:53.800 --> 00:11:05.800
 "TO GREEK WATER: HIS HOME,"
 "MY EXILE, MY ENDLESS EXILE."

00:11:05.832 --> 00:11:10.632
 "AND HERE I HAVE LOVED"
 "HIM AND BORNE HIM SONS;"

00:11:10.664 --> 00:11:13.700
 "AND THIS... MAN..."

00:11:13.732 --> 00:11:17.764
 "HAS LEFT ME AND TAKEN CREON'S"
 "DAUGHTER, TO ENJOY HER FORTUNE,"

00:11:17.800 --> 00:11:22.664
 "AND PUT ASIDE HER SOFT YELLOW"
 "HAIR AND KISS HER YOUNG MOUTH."

00:11:22.700 --> 00:11:24.632
 "SHE IS TERRIBLE."

00:11:24.664 --> 00:11:27.000
 "STONE WITH STONE EYES."

00:11:27.032 --> 00:11:30.564
 "SHE IS PITIABLE; SHE IS"
 "UNDER GREAT INJURIES."

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:33.300
 "I DO NOT KNOW HOW MUCH A"
 "GREEK WOMAN WILL ENDURE."

00:11:33.332 --> 00:11:36.300
 "THE PEOPLE OF MY RACE ARE"
 "SOMEWHAT RASH AND INTEMPERATE."

00:11:36.332 --> 00:11:41.432
 "AS FOR ME, I WANT"
 "SIMPLY TO DIE."

00:11:41.464 --> 00:11:44.900
 "BUT JASON IS NOT TO SMILE"
 "AT HIS BRIDE OVER MY GRAVE,"

00:11:44.932 --> 00:11:47.400
 "NOR THAT GREAT MAN"
 "CREON HANG WREATHS"

00:11:47.432 --> 00:11:49.764
 "AND MAKE A FEAST-DAY"
 "IN CORINTH."

00:11:49.800 --> 00:11:53.300
 "OH LET THE WREATHS BE"
 "BRIGHT BLINDING FIRE,"

00:11:53.332 --> 00:11:56.900
 "AND THE SONGS A HIGH"
 "WAILING, AND THE WINE BLOOD."

00:11:56.932 --> 00:11:59.164
 "DAUGHTER OF"
 "SORROW, BEWARE."

00:11:59.200 --> 00:12:03.800
 "IT IS DANGEROUS TO DREAM OF"
 "WINE, IT IS WORSE TO SPEAK OF"

00:12:03.832 --> 00:12:07.032
 "WAILING OR BLOOD: FOR THE"
 "IMAGES THE MIND MAKES"

00:12:07.064 --> 00:12:09.032
 "FIND A WAY OUT,"
 "THEY WORK INTO LIFE."

00:12:09.064 --> 00:12:11.832
 "LET THEM"
 "WORK INTO LIFE!"

00:12:11.864 --> 00:12:15.200
 "THERE ARE EVILS THAT"
 "CANNOT BE CURED BY EVIL."

00:12:15.232 --> 00:12:19.364
 "PATIENCE REMAINS,"
 "AND THE GODS WATCH ALL."

00:12:19.400 --> 00:12:23.400
 "LET THEM WATCH MY"
 "ENEMIES GO DOWN IN BLOOD."

00:12:23.432 --> 00:12:27.764
 "MEDEA, BEWARE! SOME"
 "GREAT PERSON IS COMING"

00:12:27.800 --> 00:12:29.800
 "- IT IS CREON HIMSELF!"

00:12:29.832 --> 00:12:31.764
 "CREON IS COMING."

00:12:31.800 --> 00:12:33.732
 "HE IS DARK WITH ANGER."

00:12:33.764 --> 00:12:41.732
 "OH MY LADY, MY CHILD; BEND IN"
 "THIS WIND, AND NOT BE BROKEN!"

00:12:41.764 --> 00:12:46.864
 "YOU HAVE"
 "ADMIRERS, I SEE."

00:12:46.900 --> 00:12:53.432
 "MEDEA, WOMAN OF THE STONE"
 "FOREHEAD AND HATE-FILLED EYES:"

00:12:53.464 --> 00:12:56.232
 "I HAVE MADE"
 "MY DECISION."

00:12:56.264 --> 00:13:01.100
 "I HAVE DECIDED THAT YOU MUST"
 "LEAVE THIS LAND AT ONCE"

00:13:01.132 --> 00:13:04.732
 "AND GO INTO BANISHMENT,"
 "YOU WITH YOUR CHILDREN."

00:13:04.764 --> 00:13:07.664
 "I INTEND TO REMOVE A"
 "ROOT OF DISTURBANCE"

00:13:07.700 --> 00:13:09.532
 "OUT OF THE"
 "SOIL OF CORINTH."

00:13:09.564 --> 00:13:13.032
 "I WILL NOT RETURN"
 "HOME UNTIL IT IS DONE."

00:13:13.064 --> 00:13:14.532
 "BANISHMENT?"

00:13:14.564 --> 00:13:18.700
 "GO WHERE YOU MAY, MEDEA,"
 "BUT HERE YOU ABIDE NO MORE."

00:13:18.732 --> 00:13:20.700
 "I WITH MY CHILDREN?"

00:13:20.732 --> 00:13:22.932
 "I WILL NOT TAKE"
 "THEM AWAY FROM YOU."

00:13:22.964 --> 00:13:24.932
 "BECAUSE WE HAVE SUFFERED EVIL"
 "WE ARE TO SUFFER MORE EVIL."

00:13:24.964 --> 00:13:26.800
 "DEATH WAS MY WISH."

00:13:26.832 --> 00:13:31.564
 "WORDS. YOU'LL"
 "NOT BE HINDERED:"

00:13:31.600 --> 00:13:37.532
 "YOU CAN HAVE DEATH WHILE"
 "THERE ARE ROPES TO HANG BY"

00:13:37.564 --> 00:13:40.300
 "OR WAVES TO DROWN IN."

00:13:40.332 --> 00:13:42.932
 "ONLY MAKE HASTE"
 "AND LEAVE THIS LAND."

00:13:42.964 --> 00:13:44.632
 "THE CHILDREN, MY LORD...."

00:13:44.664 --> 00:13:46.700
 "WHAT ARE YOU"
 "MUTTERING?"

00:13:46.732 --> 00:13:50.864
 "NOTHING. I AM PRAYING"
 "TO MY GODS FOR WISDOM."

00:13:50.900 --> 00:13:54.032
 "AND YOU FOR MERCY."

00:13:54.064 --> 00:13:57.364
 "YOU KNOW, MY LORD,"
 "WHAT EXILE MEANS:"

00:13:57.400 --> 00:14:00.100
 "TO BEG A BREAD CRUST"
 "AND BE DERIDED;"

00:14:00.132 --> 00:14:02.364
 "PELTED WITH STONES"
 "IN THE VILLAGES."

00:14:02.400 --> 00:14:04.264
 "THE CHILDREN, MY LORD,"
 "ARE JASON'S CHILDREN."

00:14:04.300 --> 00:14:08.764
 "YOUR CHOSEN FRIEND, I BELIEVE,"
 "AND NOW EVEN CLOSER BOUND."

00:14:08.800 --> 00:14:13.232
 "AND AS FOR ME YOUR SERVANT,"
 "OH MASTER OF CORINTH,"

00:14:13.264 --> 00:14:17.564
 "WHAT HAVE I DONE?"
 "WHY MUST I BE CAST?"

00:14:17.600 --> 00:14:22.432
 "I WILL TELL YOU FRANKLY: BECAUSE"
 "YOU NOURISH RANCOROUS ILL WILL"

00:14:22.464 --> 00:14:26.764
 "TOWARD PERSONS WHOM"
 "I INTEND TO PROTECT."

00:14:26.800 --> 00:14:30.364
 "I SEND YOU OUT BEFORE YOU"
 "HAVE TIME TO DO HARM HERE."

00:14:30.400 --> 00:14:32.964
 "AND YOU ARE NOTORIOUS"
 "FOR OCCULT KNOWLEDGE:"

00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:36.164
 "SORCERY,"
 "POISONS, MAGIC."

00:14:36.200 --> 00:14:43.700
 "MEN SAY YOU CAN EVEN SING"
 "DOWN THE MOON FROM HEAVEN."

00:14:43.732 --> 00:14:51.164
 "HM? AS TO THAT I KNOW NOT."
 "I KNOW YOU ARE DANGEROUS."

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:55.632
 "YOU THREATEN MY DAUGHTER:"
 "YOU HAVE TO GO."

00:14:55.664 --> 00:15:00.932
 "BUT I WISH HER WELL, MY LORD!"
 "I WISH HER ALL HAPPINESS."

00:15:00.964 --> 00:15:06.264
 "I HOPE THAT JASON MAY BE"
 "AS KIND TO HER AS TO ME."

00:15:06.300 --> 00:15:08.600
 "THAT IS YOUR WISH?"

00:15:08.632 --> 00:15:14.100
 "I MISSPOKE... I"
 "THOUGHT OF OLD DAYS."

00:15:14.132 --> 00:15:20.500
 "I ACKNOWLEDGE, MEDEA, YOU"
 "HAVE SOME CAUSE FOR GRIEF."

00:15:20.532 --> 00:15:24.200
 "I ALL THE MORE MUST GUARD"
 "AGAINST YOUR DARK WISDOM"

00:15:24.232 --> 00:15:26.100
 "AND BITTER HEART."

00:15:26.132 --> 00:15:27.864
 "YOU MISJUDGE"
 "ME CRUELLY."

00:15:27.900 --> 00:15:30.132
 "IT IS TRUE I HAVE SOME"
 "KNOWLEDGE OF DRUGS"

00:15:30.164 --> 00:15:32.532
 "AND MEDICINES: IF ANY"
 "PERSON KNOWS A LITTLE MORE"

00:15:32.564 --> 00:15:34.832
 "THAN THE COMMON MAN,"
 "THE PEOPLE SUSPECT HIM."

00:15:34.864 --> 00:15:37.932
 "BUT YOU ARE NOT A COMMON"
 "MAN, LORD OF CORINTH,"

00:15:37.964 --> 00:15:40.864
 "YOU WILL NOT"
 "FEAR KNOWLEDGE."

00:15:40.900 --> 00:15:47.700
 "NO. NOR CHANGE"
 "MY DECISION."

00:15:47.732 --> 00:15:53.164
 "I PITY YOU MEDEA,"
 "BUT YOU MUST GO."

00:15:53.200 --> 00:15:58.464
 "YOU PITY ME?"
 "YOU PITY ME?"

00:15:58.500 --> 00:16:02.700
 "I WILL ENDURE A DOG'S PITY"
 "OR A WART-GROWN TOAD'S."

00:16:02.732 --> 00:16:05.664
 "MAY GOD WHO HEARS ME..."

00:16:05.700 --> 00:16:10.632
 "WE SHALL SEE IN THE"
 "END WHO'S TO BE PITIED!"

00:16:10.664 --> 00:16:18.200
 "THIS IS GOOD. THIS"
 "IS WHAT I DESIRE."

00:16:18.232 --> 00:16:22.000
 "UNMASK THE LIVID"
 "FACE OF YOUR HATRED"

00:16:22.032 --> 00:16:24.164
 "AND I SEE WHOM"
 "I DEAL WITH."

00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:28.232
 "SERPENT AND WOLF:"
 "A WOLF FROM ASIA."

00:16:28.264 --> 00:16:32.500
 "I'D RATHER HAVE YOU RAGE"
 "NOW THAN DO HARM LATER."

00:16:32.532 --> 00:16:34.800
 "NOW, MEDEA!"
 "OUT OF HERE"

00:16:34.832 --> 00:16:37.032
 "BEFORE MY MEN"
 "DRIVE YOU OUT."

00:16:37.064 --> 00:16:39.432
 "YOU SEE A WOMAN DRIVEN"
 "HALF MAD WITH SORROW,"

00:16:39.464 --> 00:16:41.700
 "LABORING TO SAVE"
 "HER LITTLE CHILDREN."

00:16:41.732 --> 00:16:43.800
 "NO WOLF, MY LORD."

00:16:43.832 --> 00:16:48.732
 "THE RACES OF ASIA ARE HUMAN"
 "TOO, AS THE BRIGHT GREEKS ARE."

00:16:48.764 --> 00:16:53.732
 "AND WE HAVE CHILDREN AND"
 "LOVE THEM, AS GREEKS DO."

00:16:53.764 --> 00:16:58.100
 "YOU HAVE A DAUGHTER,"
 "SIR... SHE IS BEAUTIFUL."

00:16:58.132 --> 00:17:04.564
 "IF I WERE NEAR HER I"
 "WOULD SOON LOVE HER."

00:17:04.600 --> 00:17:12.400
 "YOU CAN SPEAK SWEETLY"
 "ENOUGH, YOU CAN MAKE HONEY"

00:17:12.432 --> 00:17:18.532
 "IN YOUR MOUTH LIKE A BROWN"
 "BEE WHEN IT SERVES YOUR TURN."

00:17:18.564 --> 00:17:22.832
 "NOT HONEY: THE TRUTH."

00:17:22.864 --> 00:17:29.200
 "TRUST YOU OR NOT, YOU ARE GOING"
 "OUT OF THIS COUNTRY, MEDEA."

00:17:29.232 --> 00:17:33.232
 "MAKE READY QUICKLY: I"
 "HAVE A GUEST IN MY HOUSE,"

00:17:33.264 --> 00:17:35.900
 "I SHOULD"
 "RETURN TO HIM."

00:17:35.932 --> 00:17:39.100
 "WHAT GUEST? OH MY LADY,"
 "ASK HIM WHO IS THE GUEST?"

00:17:39.132 --> 00:17:41.800
 "IF POWERFUL AND FRIENDLY"
 "HE MIGHT BE A REFUGE TO US"

00:17:41.832 --> 00:17:44.232
 "IN BITTER EXILE."

00:17:44.264 --> 00:17:46.032
 "I KNOW THAT YOUR"
 "WILL IS GRANITE."

00:17:46.064 --> 00:17:48.400
 "BUT EVEN ON THE HARSH"
 "FACE OF A GRANITE MOUNTAIN"

00:17:48.432 --> 00:17:50.464
 "SOME FLOWERS OF MERCY"
 "MAY GROW IN SEASON."

00:17:50.500 --> 00:17:52.732
 "HAVE MERCY ON MY"
 "LITTLE SONS, CREON,"

00:17:52.764 --> 00:17:54.932
 "THOUGH THERE"
 "IS NONE FOR ME."

00:17:54.964 --> 00:17:58.032
 "HOW LONG, WOMAN? THIS IS"
 "DECIDED; DONE; FINISHED."

00:17:58.064 --> 00:18:02.564
 "I AM NOT A BEGGAR. I"
 "WILL NOT TROUBLE YOU."

00:18:02.600 --> 00:18:05.932
 "I SHALL NOT"
 "LIVE LONG."

00:18:05.964 --> 00:18:10.600
 "SIRE: GRANT ME A FEW HOURS"
 "YET, ONE DAY TO PREPARE IN,"

00:18:10.632 --> 00:18:14.932
 "ONE LITTLE DAY BEFORE I GO"
 "OUT OF CORINTH FOREVER."

00:18:14.964 --> 00:18:21.532
 "WHAT? NO! I TOLD YOU THE DAY"
 "IS TODAY, MEDEA, THIS DAY."

00:18:21.564 --> 00:18:23.464
 "AND THE HOUR IS NOW."

00:18:23.500 --> 00:18:26.100
 "THERE ARE NO FLOWERS"
 "ON THIS MOUNTAIN:"

00:18:26.132 --> 00:18:29.032
 "NOT ONE VIOLET,"
 "NOT ONE ANEMONE."

00:18:29.064 --> 00:18:32.464
 "YOUR FACE, MY"
 "LORD, IS LIKE FLINT."

00:18:32.500 --> 00:18:37.200
 "IF I COULD FIND THE RIGHT WORDS,"
 "IF SOME GOD WOULD LEND ME"

00:18:37.232 --> 00:18:40.432
 "A TOUCH OF ELOQUENCE,"
 "I'D SHOW YOU MY HEART."

00:18:40.464 --> 00:18:44.500
 "I'D LIFT IT OUT OF MY BREAST"
 "AND TURN IT OVER IN MY HANDS,"

00:18:44.532 --> 00:18:47.432
 "YOU'D SEE HOW PURE IT IS"
 "OF ANY HARM OR MALICE"

00:18:47.464 --> 00:18:49.900
 "TOWARD YOU OR"
 "YOUR HOUSEHOLD."

00:18:49.932 --> 00:18:55.164
 "I BESEECH YOU, CREON, BY"
 "THE SOFT YELLOW HAIR"

00:18:55.200 --> 00:18:59.432
 "AND COOL SMOOTH FOREHEAD"
 "AND THE WHITE KNEES"

00:18:59.464 --> 00:19:02.664
 "OF THAT YOUNG GIRL WHO"
 "IS NOW JASON'S BRIDE:"

00:19:02.700 --> 00:19:08.132
 "LEND ME THIS INCH OF TIME:"
 "ONE DAY, HALF A DAY,"

00:19:08.164 --> 00:19:12.164
 "FOR THIS ONE IS NOW HALF GONE,"
 "AND I WILL GO MY SAD COURSE"

00:19:12.200 --> 00:19:15.432
 "AND VANISH IN THE MORNING"
 "QUIETLY AS DEW THAT DROPS"

00:19:15.464 --> 00:19:18.900
 "ON THE STONES AT DAWN"
 "AND IS DRY AT SUNRISE."

00:19:18.932 --> 00:19:24.164
 "YOU WILL NEVER AGAIN BE TROUBLED"
 "BY ANY WORD OR ACT OF MINE."

00:19:24.200 --> 00:19:33.100
 "AND THIS I PRAY YOU FOR"
 "YOUR DEAR CHILD'S SAKE."

00:19:33.132 --> 00:19:50.632
 "OH CREON, WHAT IS HALF A DAY IN"
 "ALL THE RICH YEARS OF CORINTH?"

00:19:50.664 --> 00:19:55.432
 "I AM NO TYRANT."

00:19:55.464 --> 00:20:02.332
 "I HAVE BEEN MERCIFUL TO"
 "MY OWN HURT, MANY TIMES."

00:20:02.364 --> 00:20:07.800
 "EVEN TO MYSELF I SEEM FOOLISH"
 "IF I GRANT YOU THIS THING."

00:20:07.832 --> 00:20:13.800
 "NO, MEDEA, I"
 "WILL NOT GRANT IT."

00:20:13.832 --> 00:20:22.100
 "WELL, WE SHALL WATCH YOU:"
 "AS A HAWK DOES A VIPER."

00:20:22.132 --> 00:20:28.132
 "WHAT HARM COULD SHE DO"
 "IN THE TAIL OF ONE DAY?"

00:20:28.164 --> 00:20:31.800
 "A RULER OUGHT TO BE"
 "RUTHLESS, BUT I AM NOT."

00:20:31.832 --> 00:20:37.500
 "I AM A FOOL IN MY OWN EYES,"
 "WHATEVER THE WORLD MAY THINK."

00:20:37.532 --> 00:20:41.632
 "TAKE IT THEN. MAKE"
 "YOUR PREPARATIONS."

00:20:41.664 --> 00:20:48.800
 "BUT IF TOMORROW'S SUN SHINES"
 "ON YOU HERE - MEDEA, YOU DIE."

00:20:48.832 --> 00:20:51.232
 "ENOUGH WORDS."
 "THANK ME NOT."

00:20:51.264 --> 00:20:57.200
 "I WANT MY HANDS"
 "WASHED OF THIS BUSINESS."

00:21:03.200 --> 00:21:05.632
 "I WILL THANK YOU..."

00:21:05.664 --> 00:21:09.232
 "AND THE WHOLE"
 "WORLD WILL HEAR OF IT."

00:21:09.264 --> 00:21:12.232
 "I HAVE SEEN THIS"
 "MAN'S ARROGANCE,"

00:21:12.264 --> 00:21:15.064
 "I WATCHED"
 "AND HEARD HIM."

00:21:15.100 --> 00:21:18.564
 "I AM OF CORINTH, AND I SAY"
 "THAT CORINTH IS NOT WELL RULED."

00:21:18.600 --> 00:21:21.632
 "THE CITY WHERE EVEN A"
 "WOMAN, EVEN A FOREIGNER,"

00:21:21.664 --> 00:21:26.000
 "SUFFERS UNJUSTLY THE RODS"
 "OF POWER IS NOT WELL RULED."

00:21:26.032 --> 00:21:30.564
 "UNHAPPY MEDEA, WHAT"
 "HAVEN, WHAT SANCTUARY,"

00:21:30.600 --> 00:21:34.032
 "WHERE WILL"
 "YOU WANDER?"

00:21:34.064 --> 00:21:39.864
 "THIS MAN, THIS BARKING"
 "DOG, THIS GULLED FOOL,"

00:21:39.900 --> 00:21:43.332
 "GODS OF MY FATHER'S COUNTRY,"
 "YOU SAW ME LOW ON MY KNEES"

00:21:43.364 --> 00:21:45.532
 "BEFORE THE GREAT"
 "DOG OF CORINTH;"

00:21:45.564 --> 00:21:48.832
 "HUMBLE, HOLDING MY HEART IN"
 "MY HANDS FOR A DOG TO BITE."

00:21:48.864 --> 00:21:56.200
 "BREAK THIS DOG'S TEETH!"

00:22:01.800 --> 00:22:06.700
 "WOMEN... IT IS A BITTER"
 "THING TO BE A WOMAN."

00:22:06.732 --> 00:22:10.532
 "A WOMAN IS WEAK FOR WARFARE,"
 "SHE MUST USE CUNNING."

00:22:10.564 --> 00:22:14.800
 "MEN BOAST THEIR BATTLES: I"
 "TELL YOU THIS, AND WE KNOW IT:"

00:22:14.832 --> 00:22:18.732
 "IT IS EASIER TO STAND IN BATTLE"
 "THREE TIMES IN THE FRONT LINE"

00:22:18.764 --> 00:22:22.132
 "IN THE STABBING FURY"
 "THAN TO BEAR ONE CHILD."

00:22:22.164 --> 00:22:25.032
 "AND A WOMAN, THEY SAY, CAN"
 "DO NO GOOD BUT IN CHILDBIRTH."

00:22:25.064 --> 00:22:26.764
 "IT MAY BE SO."

00:22:26.800 --> 00:22:31.700
 "SHE CAN DO EVIL,"
 "SHE CAN DO EVIL."

00:22:31.732 --> 00:22:35.832
 "I WEPT BEFORE THAT TALL DOG,"
 "I WEPT MY TEARS BEFORE HIM,"

00:22:35.864 --> 00:22:39.432
 "I DEGRADED MY KNEES TO HIM,"
 "I GULLED AND FLATTERED HIM:"

00:22:39.464 --> 00:22:42.932
 "OH TRIPLE FOOL, HE HAS"
 "GIVEN ME ALL THAT I NEEDED:"

00:22:42.964 --> 00:22:46.500
 "A LITTLE TIME, A"
 "SPACE OF TIME."

00:22:46.532 --> 00:22:52.464
 "DEATH IS DEARER TO ME THAN WHAT"
 "I AM NOW; AND IF TODAY BY SUNSET"

00:22:52.500 --> 00:22:58.864
 "THE WORLD HAS NOT TURNED, AND"
 "TURNED SHARP TOO, LET YOUR DOG"

00:22:58.900 --> 00:23:02.200
 "CREON SEND TWO OR THREE"
 "SLAVES TO KILL ME AND A CORD"

00:23:02.232 --> 00:23:06.832
 "TO STRANGLE ME: I WILL"
 "STRETCH OUT MY THROAT TO IT."

00:23:06.864 --> 00:23:09.900
 "BUT I HAVE A BITTER"
 "HOPE, WOMEN."

00:23:09.932 --> 00:23:13.132
 "I BEGIN TO SEE LIGHT"
 "THROUGH THE DARK WOOD,"

00:23:13.164 --> 00:23:15.900
 "BETWEEN THE MONSTROUS"
 "TRUNKS OF THE TREES,"

00:23:15.932 --> 00:23:20.032
 "AT THE END OF THE TANGLED"
 "FOREST AN EYEHOLE,"

00:23:20.064 --> 00:23:22.700
 "A PIN-POINT OF LIGHT:"

00:23:22.732 --> 00:23:26.300
 "I SHALL NOT DIE PERHAPS"
 "AS A PIGEON DIES."

00:23:26.332 --> 00:23:30.200
 "NOR LIKE AN INNOCENT LAMB"
 "THAT FEELS A HAND ON ITS HEAD"

00:23:30.232 --> 00:23:34.064
 "AND LOOKS UP FROM THE KNIFE"
 "TO THE MAN'S FACE AND DIES."

00:23:34.100 --> 00:23:39.332
 "NO, LIKE SOME YELLOW-EYED BEAST"
 "THAT HAS KILLED ITS HUNTERS"

00:23:39.364 --> 00:23:44.600
 "LET ME LIE DOWN ON THE HOUNDS'"
 "BODIES AND THE BROKEN SPEARS."

00:23:44.632 --> 00:23:48.800
 "THEN HOW TO STRIKE THEM?"
 "WHAT MEANS TO USE?"

00:23:48.832 --> 00:23:51.600
 "THERE ARE SO MANY DOORS"
 "THROUGH WHICH PAINFUL DEATH"

00:23:51.632 --> 00:23:53.900
 "MAY GLIDE IN AND CATCH..."

00:23:53.932 --> 00:23:58.732
 "WHICH ONE, WHICH ONE?"

00:24:01.364 --> 00:24:06.064
 "TELL ME: DO YOU KNOW WHAT"
 "GUEST IS IN CREON'S HOUSE?"

00:24:06.100 --> 00:24:09.200
 "AN ATHENIAN SHIP CAME"
 "FROM THE NORTH LAST NIGHT:"

00:24:09.232 --> 00:24:11.432
 "IT IS AEGEUS, THE"
 "LORD OF ATHENS."

00:24:11.464 --> 00:24:14.732
 "AEGEUS! MY LADY KNOWS HIM:"
 "I BELIEVE HE WILL HELP US."

00:24:14.764 --> 00:24:17.564
 "SOME GOD HAS BROUGHT"
 "HIM HERE, SOME SAVIOR GOD."

00:24:17.600 --> 00:24:19.932
 "HE IS LEAVING,"
 "I THINK, TODAY."

00:24:19.964 --> 00:24:23.764
 "MY LADY! LORD AEGEUS IS HERE"
 "IN CORINTH, CREON'S GUEST."

00:24:23.800 --> 00:24:26.964
 "IF YOU WILL SEE HIM AND SPEAK"
 "HIM FAIRLY, WE HAVE A REFUGE."

00:24:27.000 --> 00:24:28.764
 "I HAVE THINGS IN MY"
 "HAND TO DO. BE QUIET."

00:24:28.800 --> 00:24:30.732
 "OH, LISTEN TO ME!"

00:24:30.764 --> 00:24:32.700
 "YOU ARE DRIVEN OUT OF CORINTH,"
 "YOU MUST FIND SHELTER."

00:24:32.732 --> 00:24:34.432
 "AEGEUS OF"
 "ATHENS IS HERE."

00:24:34.464 --> 00:24:36.264
 "WHAT'S THAT TO ME?"

00:24:36.300 --> 00:24:39.100
 "I HELD YOU IN MY ARMS"
 "WHEN YOU WERE THIS LONG."

00:24:39.132 --> 00:24:41.532
 "I GAVE YOU MILK"
 "FROM THESE BREASTS"

00:24:41.564 --> 00:24:43.364
 "THAT ARE NOW"
 "DEAD LEAVES."

00:24:43.400 --> 00:24:47.600
 "I SAW THE LITTLE BEAUTIFUL BODY"
 "STRAIGHTEN AND GROW TALL:"

00:24:47.632 --> 00:24:53.532
 "OH CHILD, HOW CAN I"
 "NOT TRY TO SAVE YOU?"

00:24:53.564 --> 00:24:55.600
 "LIFE IS BETTER"
 "THAN DEATH."

00:24:55.632 --> 00:24:57.532
 "NOT NOW."

00:24:57.564 --> 00:24:59.300
 "TIME'S RUNNING OUT."

00:24:59.332 --> 00:25:03.164
 "I HAVE TIME."
 "OH, I HAVE TIME."

00:25:03.200 --> 00:25:07.864
 "IT WOULD BE GOOD TO SIT HERE A"
 "THOUSAND YEARS AND THINK OF"

00:25:07.900 --> 00:25:12.264
 "NOTHING BUT THE DEATHS"
 "OF THREE PERSONS."

00:25:12.300 --> 00:25:15.064
 "AH, THERE'S"
 "NO HOPE THEN."

00:25:15.100 --> 00:25:18.564
 "CHILD, IF YOU WOULD DO"
 "THIS RED THING YOU DREAM OF,"

00:25:18.600 --> 00:25:21.032
 "ALL CORINTH WOULD"
 "POUR AGAINST YOU."

00:25:21.064 --> 00:25:23.164
 "AFTER MY ENEMIES ARE"
 "PUNISHED AND I'VE HEARD"

00:25:23.200 --> 00:25:26.364
 "THE LAST BROKEN MOAN"
 "- CORINTH? WHAT'S THAT?"

00:25:26.400 --> 00:25:32.100
 "I'LL SLEEP. I'LL"
 "SLEEP WELL."

00:25:32.132 --> 00:25:40.232
 "I AM ALONE AGAINST ALL AND"
 "SO WEARY THAT IT IS PITIFUL."

00:25:43.532 --> 00:25:45.532
 "LOOK: WHO IS COMING?"

00:25:45.564 --> 00:25:48.264
 "I SEE SUNLIGHT"
 "GLITTER ON LANCEHEADS."

00:25:48.300 --> 00:25:50.232
 "OH, IT IS JASON!"

00:25:50.264 --> 00:25:52.700
 "JASON! MEDEA'S"
 "WORST ENEMY,"

00:25:52.732 --> 00:25:55.264
 "WHO SHOULD HAVE BEEN"
 "HER DEAREST PROTECTOR."

00:25:59.900 --> 00:26:03.332
 "WHAT BUSINESS HAVE"
 "YOU HERE, YOU WOMEN"

00:26:03.364 --> 00:26:06.900
 "CLUSTERED LIKE BUZZING"
 "BEES AROUND A HIVE DOOR?"

00:26:06.932 --> 00:26:09.400
 "WHERE IS MEDEA?"

00:26:09.432 --> 00:26:15.732
 "THERE: MOURNING FOR"
 "WHAT YOU HAVE DONE."

00:26:15.764 --> 00:26:19.532
 "WHAT SHE"
 "HAS DONE. NOT I."

00:26:19.564 --> 00:26:26.232
 "NOT BY MY WILL SHE AND"
 "MY SONS ARE EXILED."

00:26:26.264 --> 00:26:30.032
 "IS THERE ANOTHER"
 "DOG HERE?"

00:26:30.064 --> 00:26:33.364
 "SO, MEDEA... YOU"
 "HAVE ONCE MORE"

00:26:33.400 --> 00:26:36.832
 "AFFRONTED AND INSULTED"
 "THE HEAD OF CORINTH."

00:26:36.864 --> 00:26:41.264
 "THIS IS NOT THE FIRST TIME I'VE"
 "SEEN WHAT A FOOL ANGER IS."

00:26:41.300 --> 00:26:43.732
 "YOU MIGHT HAVE LIVED HERE"
 "HAPPILY, SECURE AND HONORED"

00:26:43.764 --> 00:26:46.364
 "- I HOPED YOU WOULD -"
 "BY BEING JUST A LITTLE"

00:26:46.400 --> 00:26:49.564
 "DECENTLY RESPECTFUL"
 "TOWARD THOSE IN POWER."

00:26:49.600 --> 00:26:51.600
 "INSTEAD YOU HAD TO"
 "GO MAD WITH ANGER"

00:26:51.632 --> 00:26:54.832
 "AND TALK"
 "YOURSELF INTO EXILE."

00:26:54.864 --> 00:26:58.432
 "TO ME IT MATTERS LITTLE"
 "WHAT YOU SAY ABOUT ME,"

00:26:58.464 --> 00:27:01.632
 "BUT RULERS"
 "ARE SENSITIVE."

00:27:01.664 --> 00:27:05.900
 "CALL YOURSELF LUCKY, MEDEA,"
 "NOT TO GET WORSE THAN EXILE."

00:27:05.932 --> 00:27:09.332
 "IN SPITE OF ALL THIS, I HAVE"
 "YOUR INTEREST AT HEART"

00:27:09.364 --> 00:27:11.964
 "AND AM HERE"
 "TO HELP YOU."

00:27:12.000 --> 00:27:14.632
 "EXILE'S A BITTER"
 "BUSINESS,"

00:27:14.664 --> 00:27:17.132
 "I WANT TO MAKE SOME"
 "PROVISION FOR YOU."

00:27:17.164 --> 00:27:20.664
 "I WISH YOU NO HARM,"
 "ALTHOUGH YOU HATE ME."

00:27:20.700 --> 00:27:26.500
 "AND IN PARTICULAR THE"
 "CHILDREN; MY SONS; OUR SONS."

00:27:26.532 --> 00:27:29.000
 "YOU MIGHT HAVE"
 "BEEN DECENT ENOUGH"

00:27:29.032 --> 00:27:31.632
 "TO HAVE THOUGHT"
 "OF OUR SONS."

00:27:31.664 --> 00:27:35.500
 "DID YOU CONSIDER THEM WHEN"
 "YOU BETRAYED THIS HOUSE?"

00:27:35.532 --> 00:27:37.632
 "CERTAINLY I"
 "CONSIDERED THEM."

00:27:37.664 --> 00:27:39.664
 "IT WAS MY HOPE THAT THEY"
 "WOULD GROW UP HERE, AND I,"

00:27:39.700 --> 00:27:42.332
 "HAVING MARRIED POWER,"
 "COULD PROTECT AND FAVOR THEM."

00:27:42.364 --> 00:27:45.000
 "AND IF PERHAPS, AFTER MANY"
 "YEARS, I BECOME DYNAST OF"

00:27:45.032 --> 00:27:49.032
 "CORINTH - FOR THAT IS CREON'S"
 "DESIRE, TO MAKE ME HIS HEIR -"

00:27:49.064 --> 00:27:52.500
 "OUR SONS WOULD HAVE"
 "BEEN A KING'S SONS."

00:27:52.532 --> 00:27:56.732
 "I HOPED TO HELP THEM, WHEREVER"
 "THEY GO: BUT NOW OF COURSE"

00:27:56.764 --> 00:28:00.232
 "MUST LOOK FORWARD"
 "TO YOUNGER CHILDREN."

00:28:00.264 --> 00:28:03.232
 "AH, IT'S ENOUGH."
 "SOMETHING MIGHT HAPPEN."

00:28:03.264 --> 00:28:05.600
 "IT IS LIKELY THAT"
 "SOMETHING MIGHT HAPPEN"

00:28:05.632 --> 00:28:07.532
 "TO THE BRIDE"
 "AND THE MARRIAGE."

00:28:07.564 --> 00:28:09.132
 "I'LL GUARD AGAINST IT."

00:28:09.164 --> 00:28:11.664
 "BUT EVIDENTLY CREON IS"
 "RIGHT TO BE RID OF YOU."

00:28:11.700 --> 00:28:13.532
 "I'LL GO TO THE PALACE"
 "AND SEEK FOR AEGEUS"

00:28:13.564 --> 00:28:15.364
 "- THERE'S NO OTHER HOPE."

00:28:15.400 --> 00:28:17.464
 "HAVE YOU"
 "FINISHED NOW?"

00:28:17.500 --> 00:28:22.132
 "I THOUGHT I WOULD LET YOU SPEAK"
 "ON AND SPREAD OUT YOUR"

00:28:22.164 --> 00:28:25.632
 "SHAMELESSNESS BEFORE THESE"
 "WOMEN: THE WAY A TYRIAN TRADER"

00:28:25.664 --> 00:28:30.664
 "UNROLLS HIS RARE FABRICS:"
 ""DO YOU LIKE IT, LADIES?""

00:28:30.700 --> 00:28:35.000
 "IT IS THE DOG'S"
 "DAUGHTER'S HUSBAND."

00:28:35.032 --> 00:28:40.500
 "IT IS A BRAVE PERSON: IT HAS"
 "FINALLY GOT UP ITS COURAGE"

00:28:40.532 --> 00:28:45.400
 "- WITH A GUARD OF SPEARS - TO"
 "COME AND LOOK ME IN THE FACE."

00:28:45.432 --> 00:28:53.264
 "OH JASON: HOW HAVE"
 "YOU PULLED ME DOWN"

00:28:53.300 --> 00:28:57.400
 "TO THIS HELL OF"
 "VILE THOUGHTS?"

00:28:57.432 --> 00:29:02.264
 "I DID NOT USE TO TALK"
 "LIKE A COMMON WOMAN."

00:29:02.300 --> 00:29:10.964
 "I LOVED YOU ONCE: AND I AM"
 "ASHAMED OF IT: BUT THERE ARE"

00:29:11.000 --> 00:29:14.632
 "SOME THINGS THAT OUGHT TO BE"
 "REMEMBERED BY YOU AND ME."

00:29:14.664 --> 00:29:18.364
 "THAT BLUE DAY WHEN WE"
 "DROVE THROUGH THE HELLESPONT"

00:29:18.400 --> 00:29:23.264
 "INTO GREEK SEA, AND THE"
 "GREAT-SHOULDERED HEROES"

00:29:23.300 --> 00:29:28.332
 "WERE SINGING AT THE OARS,"
 "AND THOSE BIRDS WERE FLYING"

00:29:28.364 --> 00:29:34.700
 "THROUGH THE BLOWN FOAM: THAT"
 "DAY WAS TOO FINE I SUPPOSE"

00:29:34.732 --> 00:29:38.232
 "FOR CREON'S DAUGHTER'S"
 "MAN TO REMEMBER:"

00:29:38.264 --> 00:29:42.064
 "BUT YOU MIGHT REMEMBER WHETHER"
 "I CHEATED MY FATHER FOR YOU"

00:29:42.100 --> 00:29:45.400
 "AND TAMED THE FIRE-BREATHING"
 "BRAZEN-HOOFED BULLS;"

00:29:45.432 --> 00:29:48.764
 "AND WHETHER I SAVED YOUR LIFE"
 "IN THE FIELD OF THE TEETH;"

00:29:48.800 --> 00:29:52.332
 "AND YOU MIGHT REMEMBER WHETHER"
 "I POISONED THE GREAT SERPENT"

00:29:52.364 --> 00:29:55.764
 "AND GOT YOU THE GOLDEN"
 "FLEECE; AND FLED WITH YOU,"

00:29:55.800 --> 00:29:58.500
 "AND KILLED MY BROTHER"
 "WHEN HE PURSUED US,"

00:29:58.532 --> 00:30:01.732
 "MAKING MYSELF ABOMINABLE"
 "IN MY OWN HOME;"

00:30:01.764 --> 00:30:06.132
 "AND THEN IN YOURS I"
 "GOT YOUR ENEMY PELIAS"

00:30:06.164 --> 00:30:09.100
 "HACKED TO DEATH BY HIS"
 "OWN DAUGHTER'S HANDS."

00:30:09.132 --> 00:30:12.900
 "WHATEVER THESE FINE"
 "CORINTHIAN FRIENDS OF YOURS"

00:30:12.932 --> 00:30:15.232
 "MAY SAY AGAINST MY"
 "RAPID AND TRICKY WISDOM;"

00:30:15.264 --> 00:30:18.964
 "YOU IT HAS SERVED,"
 "YOU IT HAS SERVED WELL:"

00:30:19.000 --> 00:30:22.464
 "HERE ARE FIVE TIMES,"
 "IF I'VE COUNTED RIGHT -"

00:30:22.500 --> 00:30:25.732
 "AND ALL'S NOT COUNTED"
 "- WHERE YOUR ADVENTURES"

00:30:25.764 --> 00:30:29.900
 "WOULD HAVE BEEN DUSTY"
 "DEATH IF I'D NOT SAVED YOU."

00:30:29.932 --> 00:30:34.000
 "BUT NOW YOU THINK YOUR"
 "ADVENTURES ARE OVER;"

00:30:34.032 --> 00:30:38.764
 "YOU ARE SAFE AND"
 "HIGH PLACED IN CORINTH,"

00:30:38.800 --> 00:30:43.532
 "AND WILL NEED"
 "ME NO MORE."

00:30:43.564 --> 00:30:46.900
 "IT IS A BIT OF A DOG,"
 "ISN'T IT, WOMEN?"

00:30:46.932 --> 00:30:51.664
 "IT IS WELL QUALIFIED TO SLEEP"
 "WITH THE DOG'S DAUGHTER."

00:30:51.700 --> 00:30:57.932
 "BUT FOR ME, JASON, ME"
 "DRIVEN BY THE HAIRY SNOUTS"

00:30:57.964 --> 00:31:01.000
 "FROM THE QUADRUPED"
 "MARRIAGE BED,"

00:31:01.032 --> 00:31:06.600
 "WHAT REFUGE DOES YOUR"
 "PRUDENT KINDNESS ADVISE?"

00:31:06.632 --> 00:31:10.964
 "THE WORLD IS A LITTLE"
 "CLOSED TO ME, AH?"

00:31:11.000 --> 00:31:14.400
 "BY THE THINGS I"
 "HAVE DONE FOR YOU."

00:31:14.432 --> 00:31:17.532
 "I SEE, MEDEA, YOU HAVE"
 "BEEN A VERY CAREFUL"

00:31:17.564 --> 00:31:19.500
 "MERCHANT OF BENEFITS."

00:31:19.532 --> 00:31:22.864
 "YOU FORGET NONE, YOU"
 "KEEP A STRICT RECKONING."

00:31:22.900 --> 00:31:26.000
 "BUT, SOME LITTLE THINGS THAT I"
 "ON MY SIDE HAVE DONE FOR YOU"

00:31:26.032 --> 00:31:30.132
 "OUGHT TO BE IN THE BOOKS TOO:"
 "FOR EXAMPLE, I CARRIED YOU"

00:31:30.164 --> 00:31:34.164
 "OUT OF THE DIRT AND SUPERSTITION"
 "OF ASIATIC COLCHIS"

00:31:34.200 --> 00:31:36.832
 "INTO THE RATIONAL SUNLIGHT OF"
 "GREECE, AND THE MARBLE MUSIC"

00:31:36.864 --> 00:31:39.800
 "OF THE GREEK TEMPLES:"
 "IS THAT NO BENEFIT?"

00:31:39.832 --> 00:31:42.800
 "I HAVE BROUGHT YOU TO MEET"
 "THE FIRST MINDS OF OUR TIME,"

00:31:42.832 --> 00:31:45.532
 "AND TO SPEAK AS AN EQUAL"
 "WITH THE GREAT HEROES"

00:31:45.564 --> 00:31:48.800
 "AND RULERS OF CITIES:"
 "IS THAT NO BENEFIT?"

00:31:48.832 --> 00:31:55.900
 "HERE YOU ARE FAMOUS. WHO"
 "WOULD HAVE SPOKEN YOUR NAME"

00:31:55.932 --> 00:32:00.100
 "HAD YOUR DAYS RUN BY ON"
 "THAT LAST EDGE OF THE WORLD?"

00:32:00.132 --> 00:32:03.032
 "THAT BLOOD AND FILTH"
 "I SAVED YOU FROM,"

00:32:03.064 --> 00:32:05.700
 "SO THAT ONE DAY YOU MAY"
 "VENT ON ME THIS VIOLENCE,"

00:32:05.732 --> 00:32:09.232
 "THIS BARBARIAN"
 "GRATITUDE?"

00:32:09.264 --> 00:32:12.532
 "AND NOW, THIS GRIEVOUS"
 "THING THAT YOU HATE ME FOR:"

00:32:12.564 --> 00:32:16.832
 "THAT I MARRIED CREON'S"
 "YOUNG DAUGHTER, LITTLE CREUSA:"

00:32:16.864 --> 00:32:20.464
 "DO YOU THINK I DID IT"
 "LIKE A BOY OR A WOMAN,"

00:32:20.500 --> 00:32:22.464
 "OUT OF BLIND PASSION?"

00:32:22.500 --> 00:32:25.464
 "NO, I DID IT TO ACHIEVE"
 "POWER HERE;"

00:32:25.500 --> 00:32:30.064
 "AND I'D HAVE USED THAT POWER"
 "TO PROTECT YOU AND OUR SONS,"

00:32:30.100 --> 00:32:34.900
 "BUT YOUR JEALOUS MADNESS"
 "HAS MUDDLED EVERYTHING."

00:32:34.932 --> 00:32:39.132
 "AND FINALLY: AS TO THOSE ACTS"
 "OF SERVICE YOU SO LOUDLY BOAST:"

00:32:39.164 --> 00:32:43.200
 "WHOM DO I THANK FOR THEM?"
 "I THANK DIVINE VENUS,"

00:32:43.232 --> 00:32:47.332
 "THE GODDESS WHO"
 "MAKES GIRLS FALL IN LOVE."

00:32:47.364 --> 00:32:50.164
 "YOU DID THEM BECAUSE"
 "YOU HAD TO DO THEM;"

00:32:50.200 --> 00:32:53.364
 "VENUS COMPELLED YOU;"
 "I ENJOYED HER FAVOR."

00:32:53.400 --> 00:32:57.864
 "A MAN DARES THINGS, YOU"
 "KNOW, HE MAKES HIS ADVENTURE"

00:32:57.900 --> 00:33:01.432
 "IN THE COLD EYE OF DEATH;"
 "AND IF THE GODS CARE FOR HIM"

00:33:01.464 --> 00:33:06.664
 "THEY APPOINT AN INSTRUMENT"
 "TO SAVE HIM; IF NOT, HE DIES."

00:33:06.700 --> 00:33:11.064
 "YOU WERE THAT"
 "INSTRUMENT."

00:33:11.100 --> 00:33:15.232
 "HERE IT IS:"
 "THE LOWEST."

00:33:15.264 --> 00:33:20.532
 "THE OBSCENE DREGS; THE"
 "SLIME AND THE LOATHING;"

00:33:20.564 --> 00:33:23.964
 "THE MUDDY BOTTOM"
 "OF A MOUTHED CUP:"

00:33:24.000 --> 00:33:27.464
 "WHEN A SCOUNDREL"
 "BEGINS TO INVOKE THE GODS."

00:33:27.500 --> 00:33:29.500
 "YOU HAD BETTER"
 "GO, JASON."

00:33:29.532 --> 00:33:32.232
 "VULGARITY IS A CONTAGIOUS"
 "DISEASE; AND IN A MOMENT"

00:33:32.264 --> 00:33:35.032
 "WHAT COULD I DO BUT SPIT"
 "AT YOU LIKE A PEASANT,"

00:33:35.064 --> 00:33:37.332
 "OR CURSE YOU LIKE"
 "A DRUNKEN SLAVE."

00:33:49.832 --> 00:33:59.564
 "YOU HAD BETTER TAKE YOURSELF"
 "BACK TO "LITTLE CREUSA"."

00:33:59.600 --> 00:34:03.332
 "MEDEA, I CAME TO HELP YOU"
 "AND SAVE YOU IF POSSIBLE."

00:34:03.364 --> 00:34:06.064
 "YOUR HELP IS"
 "NOT WANTED."

00:34:06.100 --> 00:34:12.532
 "GO. GO."

00:34:28.500 --> 00:34:30.700
 "I WANT TO SEE"
 "MY BOYS..."

00:34:30.732 --> 00:34:32.864
 "GO QUICKLY."

00:34:32.900 --> 00:34:37.000
 "YOURS THE"
 "REGRET THEN."

00:34:48.100 --> 00:34:50.200
 "THIS IS IT."

00:34:50.232 --> 00:34:56.664
 "I DID NOT SURELY KNOW"
 "IT: LOATHING IS ALL."

00:34:56.700 --> 00:35:00.964
 "THIS FLESH HE HAS"
 "TOUCHED AND FOULED."

00:35:01.000 --> 00:35:02.900
 "THESE HANDS THAT"
 "WROUGHT FOR HIM,"

00:35:02.932 --> 00:35:05.032
 "THESE KNEES THAT"
 "RAN HIS ERRANDS."

00:35:05.064 --> 00:35:06.932
 "THIS BODY"
 "THAT TOOK HIS..."

00:35:06.964 --> 00:35:09.832
 "WHAT THEY CALL LOVE,"
 "AND MADE CHILDREN OF IT."

00:35:09.864 --> 00:35:19.532
 "IF I COULD PEEL OFF THE FLESH,"
 "THE CHILDREN, THE MEMORY."

00:35:19.564 --> 00:35:26.532
 "WHAT IS SHE DOING, THAT WOMAN,"
 "STARING LIKE STONE, STARING?"

00:35:26.564 --> 00:35:30.164
 "OH, SHE HAS"
 "MOVED NOW."

00:35:30.200 --> 00:35:33.532
 "ANNIHILATION..."

00:35:33.564 --> 00:35:46.264
 "THE WORD IS PURE"
 "MUSIC: ANNIHILATION."

00:35:46.300 --> 00:35:50.064
 "TO ANNIHILATE THE PAST"
 "- IS NOT POSSIBLE:"

00:35:50.100 --> 00:35:55.400
 "BUT ITS FRUIT IN THE"
 "PRESENT CAN BE NIPPED OFF."

00:35:55.432 --> 00:35:59.532
 "AM I TO LOOK IN MY SONS' EYES"
 "AND SEE JASON'S FOREVER?"

00:35:59.564 --> 00:36:01.932
 "BETTER TO BE CLEAN"
 "BONES ON THE SHORE."

00:36:01.964 --> 00:36:07.264
 "WHITE BONES ON"
 "THE BLACK SEA SHORE."

00:36:07.300 --> 00:36:10.100
 "OH, BUT THAT'S FAR."

00:36:10.132 --> 00:36:15.832
 "NOT YET. CORINTH"
 "MUST HOWL FIRST."

00:36:15.864 --> 00:36:18.500
 "PEACE AND PITY"
 "ARE DEPARTED;"

00:36:18.532 --> 00:36:24.600
 "HATRED IS HERE, HATRED IS HEAVY;"
 "IT CLINGS TO THE EARTH."

00:36:24.632 --> 00:36:28.764
 "LOVE BLOWS AWAY,"
 "HATRED REMAINS."

00:36:28.800 --> 00:36:32.732
 "WOMEN HATE WAR, BUT"
 "MEN WILL WAGE IT AGAIN."

00:36:32.764 --> 00:36:36.464
 "WOMEN MAY HATE THEIR HUSBANDS,"
 "AND SONS THEIR FATHERS,"

00:36:36.500 --> 00:36:39.164
 "BUT WOMEN WILL NEVER"
 "HATE THEIR OWN CHILDREN."

00:36:39.200 --> 00:36:42.432
 "BUT AS FOR ME, I WILL"
 "DO GOOD TO MY HUSBAND,"

00:36:42.464 --> 00:36:47.264
 "I WILL LOVE MY SONS AND"
 "DAUGHTERS, AND ADORE THE GODS."

00:36:47.300 --> 00:36:49.732
 "IF I SHOULD GO INTO THE"
 "HOUSE WITH A SHARP KNIFE"

00:36:49.764 --> 00:36:52.000
 "TO THE MAN"
 "AND HIS BRIDE..."

00:36:52.032 --> 00:36:54.364
 "OR IF I COULD FIRE THE ROOM THEY"
 "SLEEP IN, AND HEAR THEM WAKE"

00:36:54.400 --> 00:36:56.632
 "IN THE WHITE OF THE FIRE,"
 "AND HOWL TO EACH OTHER,"

00:36:56.664 --> 00:36:59.800
 "AND HOWL LIKE DOGS,"
 "AND HOWL AND DIE."

00:36:59.832 --> 00:37:04.064
 "BUT I MIGHT FAIL; I"
 "MIGHT BE CUT DOWN FIRST;"

00:37:04.100 --> 00:37:07.200
 "THE KNIFE MIGHT TURN IN MY"
 "HAND, OR THE FIRE NOT BURN,"

00:37:07.232 --> 00:37:10.064
 "AND MY ENEMIES"
 "COULD LAUGH AT ME."

00:37:10.100 --> 00:37:17.100
 "NO: I HAVE SUBTLER MEANS,"
 "AND MORE DEADLY CRUEL."

00:37:17.132 --> 00:37:23.732
 "I HAVE MY DARK ART THAT"
 "FOOLS CALL WITCHCRAFT."

00:37:23.764 --> 00:37:26.632
 "NOT FOR NOTHING I HAVE"
 "WORSHIPPED THE WILD GRAY"

00:37:26.664 --> 00:37:31.032
 "GODDESS THAT WALKS IN THE DARK,"
 "THE WISE ONE, THE TERRIBLE ONE,"

00:37:31.064 --> 00:37:35.800
 "THE SWEET HUNTRESS,"
 "FLOWER OF NIGHT, HECATE,"

00:37:35.832 --> 00:37:39.500
 "IN MY HOUSE"
 "AT MY HEARTH."

00:37:39.532 --> 00:37:42.700
 "MY LADY, HE WAS LEAVING"
 "CREON'S DOOR: HE IS COMING."

00:37:42.732 --> 00:37:45.064
 "AEGEUS IS COMING!"
 "THE POWER OF ATHENS."

00:37:45.100 --> 00:37:47.564
 "I WILL NOT SEE HIM. GO"
 "BACK AND TELL HIM SO."

00:37:47.600 --> 00:37:52.600
 "ANCIENT GODDESS TO WHOM I AND"
 "MY PEOPLE MAKE THE SACRIFICE"

00:37:52.632 --> 00:37:59.132
 "OF BLACK LAMBS AND BLACK"
 "FEMALE HOUNDS, HOLY ONE,"

00:37:59.164 --> 00:38:05.900
 "HAUNTER OF CROSSROADS,"
 "QUEEN OF NIGHT, HECATE,"

00:38:05.932 --> 00:38:10.800
 "HELP ME NOW: TO REMEMBER"
 "IN MY MIND THE USE OF THE"

00:38:10.832 --> 00:38:16.464
 "VENOMOUS FIRE, THE MAGIC"
 "SONG, AND THE SHARP GEMS."

00:38:20.132 --> 00:38:24.264
 "HE IS HERE, MY LADY."
 "ATHENS IS HERE."

00:38:24.300 --> 00:38:26.364
 "REJOICE, MEDEA!"

00:38:26.400 --> 00:38:31.400
 "THERE IS NO FAIRER GREETING"
 "FROM FRIEND TO FRIEND."

00:38:31.432 --> 00:38:37.332
 "MEDEA, HAIL"
 "AND REJOICE."

00:38:37.364 --> 00:38:42.700
 "REJOICE? IT MAY BE SO."

00:38:42.732 --> 00:38:47.700
 "IT MAY BE I SHALL REJOICE"
 "BEFORE THE SUN SETS."

00:38:47.732 --> 00:38:50.464
 "MEDEA! WHAT HAS"
 "HAPPENED TO YOU?"

00:38:50.500 --> 00:38:54.364
 "NOTHING; I AM QUITE WELL:"
 "FOOLS TROUBLE ME."

00:38:54.400 --> 00:38:57.932
 "WHERE ARE YOU TRAVELING"
 "FROM, AEGEUS?"

00:38:57.964 --> 00:38:59.632
 "FROM DELPHI, WHERE"
 "I WENT TO CONSULT"

00:38:59.664 --> 00:39:02.000
 "THE ANCIENT"
 "ORACLE OF APOLLO."

00:39:02.032 --> 00:39:05.332
 "OH, DELPHI. DID YOU"
 "GET A GOOD ANSWER?"

00:39:05.364 --> 00:39:08.500
 "AN OBSCURE ONE."
 "SOME GOD OR OTHER"

00:39:08.532 --> 00:39:11.900
 "HAS MADE ME UNABLE TO BEGET"
 "A CHILD: THAT IS MY TROUBLE:"

00:39:11.932 --> 00:39:15.100
 "BUT THE ORACLE NEVER"
 "GIVES PLAIN RESPONSES."

00:39:15.132 --> 00:39:18.800
 "I TELL YOU THESE THINGS SO"
 "THAT YOU MIGHT HELP ME"

00:39:18.832 --> 00:39:21.300
 "WITH THE"
 "GOD'S MEANING."

00:39:21.332 --> 00:39:23.900
 "WHAT DID APOLLO"
 "SAY TO YOU?"

00:39:23.932 --> 00:39:27.200
 "THAT I MUST NOT UNLOOSE THE"
 "HANGING FOOT OF THE WINESKIN"

00:39:27.232 --> 00:39:30.264
 "UNTIL I RETURN TO THE"
 "HEARTH OF MY FATHERS."

00:39:30.300 --> 00:39:32.464
 "THE HANGING FOOT"
 "OF THE WINESKIN."

00:39:32.500 --> 00:39:34.832
 "YOU'VE NEVER"
 "HAD A CHILD?"

00:39:34.864 --> 00:39:37.900
 "NO, AND IT"
 "IS BITTERNESS."

00:39:37.932 --> 00:39:41.132
 "BUT WHEN MISFORTUNE COMES"
 "IT IS BITTER TO HAVE CHILDREN,"

00:39:41.164 --> 00:39:45.064
 "AND WATCH THEIR STARLIKE"
 "FACES GROW DIM TO ENDURE IT."

00:39:45.100 --> 00:39:48.564
 "WHEN DEATH COMES, MEDEA,"
 "IT IS, FOR A CHILDLESS MAN,"

00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:53.464
 "UTTER DESPAIR,"
 "DARKNESS, EXTINCTION."

00:39:53.500 --> 00:39:57.664
 "ONE'S CHILDREN ARE"
 "THE LIFE AFTER DEATH."

00:39:57.700 --> 00:40:02.800
 "DO YOU FEEL IT SO?"
 "DO YOU FEEL IT SO?"

00:40:02.832 --> 00:40:07.864
 "THEN, IF YOU HAD A DOG-EYED"
 "ENEMY AND NEEDED ABSOLUTE"

00:40:07.900 --> 00:40:12.100
 "VENGEANCE, YOU'D KILL"
 "THE MAN'S CHILDREN FIRST."

00:40:12.132 --> 00:40:16.032
 "UNCHILD HIM, HA?"
 "AND THEN UNLIFE HIM."

00:40:16.064 --> 00:40:18.600
 "I DO NOT CARE TO"
 "THINK OF SUCH HORRORS."

00:40:18.632 --> 00:40:20.400
 "I HAVE NO"
 "COMPLETE ENEMY."

00:40:20.432 --> 00:40:22.500
 "WHAT IS IT, MEDEA?"
 "WHAT'S THE MATTER?"

00:40:22.532 --> 00:40:24.664
 "I WOULD NOT HURT"
 "MY CHILDREN."

00:40:24.700 --> 00:40:27.064
 "THEIR FATHER"
 "HURTS THEM."

00:40:27.100 --> 00:40:30.132
 "WHAT DO YOU MEAN? JASON?"
 "WHAT HAS JASON DONE?"

00:40:30.164 --> 00:40:33.000
 "HE HAS CAST ME OFF AND MARRIED"
 "CREON'S YOUNG DAUGHTER."

00:40:33.032 --> 00:40:35.864
 "AND CREON, THIS VERY DAY, IS"
 "DRIVING US INTO BLACK EXILE."

00:40:35.900 --> 00:40:38.264
 "YOU MEAN YOU'RE"
 "DRIVEN OUT INTO EXILE?"

00:40:38.300 --> 00:40:39.732
 "WHY THAT?"

00:40:39.764 --> 00:40:42.832
 "BECAUSE OUR PRESENCE HERE IS"
 "EMBARRASSING TO THE YOUNG BRIDE."

00:40:42.864 --> 00:40:45.064
 "DO YOU NOT THINK SUCH MEN"
 "OUGHT TO BE PUNISHED, AEGEUS?"

00:40:45.100 --> 00:40:47.000
 "WHERE WILL YOU GO?"

00:40:47.032 --> 00:40:49.464
 "IF THERE IS ANY RIGHTNESS"
 "ON EARTH OR IN HEAVEN,"

00:40:49.500 --> 00:40:51.164
 "THEY WILL BE"
 "PUNISHED."

00:40:51.200 --> 00:40:54.032
 "WHERE WILL YOU"
 "GO TO, MEDEA?"

00:40:54.064 --> 00:40:57.564
 "WHAT? TO DEATH"
 "OF COURSE."

00:40:57.600 --> 00:41:00.764
 "OH, SHE IS ALL BEWILDERED, SIR,"
 "IN THE DEEP STORM AND OCEAN"

00:41:00.800 --> 00:41:04.132
 "OF GRIEF, OR SHE WOULD ASK"
 "OF YOU REFUGE IN ATHENS."

00:41:04.164 --> 00:41:05.932
 "AH? SO I SHOULD."

00:41:05.964 --> 00:41:10.164
 "AEGEUS, WILL YOU"
 "SHELTER ME IN ATHENS?"

00:41:10.200 --> 00:41:14.532
 "IF YOU BY YOUR OWN MEANS COME TO"
 "ATHENS I WILL TAKE CARE OF YOU."

00:41:14.564 --> 00:41:16.464
 "I COULD REPAY"
 "YOU FOR IT."

00:41:16.500 --> 00:41:18.864
 "I KNOW THE REMEDIES"
 "THAT MAKE A DRY STICK"

00:41:18.900 --> 00:41:21.100
 "FLAME INTO"
 "FLOWER AND FRUIT."

00:41:21.132 --> 00:41:23.164
 "YOU'D CURE"
 "MY STERILITY?"

00:41:23.200 --> 00:41:26.832
 "I COULD DO SO. BUT I"
 "HAVE CERTAIN ENEMIES."

00:41:26.864 --> 00:41:30.200
 "IF POWERFUL ENEMIES CAME"
 "BAYING FOR MY BLOOD"

00:41:30.232 --> 00:41:32.000
 "WOULD YOU"
 "PROTECT ME?"

00:41:32.032 --> 00:41:34.732
 "COME THE FOUR ENDS OF THE"
 "WORLD, THEY WILL NOT BREAK IN."

00:41:34.764 --> 00:41:37.000
 "YOU'RE SAFE THERE:"
 "I AM YOUR PLEDGE."

00:41:37.032 --> 00:41:38.600
 "WILL YOU SWEAR"
 "IT, AEGEUS?"

00:41:38.632 --> 00:41:40.464
 "WHY? I PROMISED."

00:41:40.500 --> 00:41:45.364
 "I TRUST YOU: THE OATH IS FORMAL:"
 "YOUR CURE DEPENDS ON IT."

00:41:45.400 --> 00:41:49.100
 "DO YOU SWEAR BY THE FRUITFUL"
 "EARTH AND HIGH SHINING HEAVEN"

00:41:49.132 --> 00:41:51.532
 "TO PROTECT ME IN"
 "ATHENS AGAINST ALL MEN?"

00:41:51.564 --> 00:41:53.432
 "I SWEAR IT."

00:41:53.464 --> 00:41:56.500
 "IF YOU SHOULD BREAK IT, THE"
 "EARTH WILL GIVE YOU NO BREAD"

00:41:56.532 --> 00:41:58.832
 "BUT DEATH, AND THE SKY"
 "NO LIGHT BUT DARKNESS."

00:41:58.864 --> 00:42:00.900
 "I WILL NOT BREAK IT."

00:42:00.932 --> 00:42:02.964
 "YOU MUST REPEAT"
 "THE WORDS, AEGEUS."

00:42:03.000 --> 00:42:07.464
 "IF I BREAK IT, THE EARTH WILL"
 "GIVE ME NO BREAD BUT DEATH,"

00:42:07.500 --> 00:42:11.732
 "AND THE SKY NO"
 "LIGHT BUT DARKNESS."

00:42:11.764 --> 00:42:19.332
 "YOU HAVE SWORN: THE"
 "GODS HAVE HEARD YOU."

00:42:23.864 --> 00:42:25.964
 "WHEN WILL YOU"
 "COME TO ATHENS?"

00:42:26.000 --> 00:42:35.664
 "TO ATHENS? WHY, IF I COME,"
 "IF I LIVE, IT WILL BE SOON."

00:42:35.700 --> 00:42:39.432
 "THE YOKE'S ON THE"
 "NECKS OF THE HORSES."

00:42:39.464 --> 00:42:42.600
 "I HAVE SOME THINGS TO"
 "DO THAT MEN WILL TALK OF"

00:42:42.632 --> 00:42:45.264
 "AFTERWARDS IN"
 "HUSHED VOICES:"

00:42:45.300 --> 00:42:53.064
 "WHILE I AND MY CHILDREN"
 "SAFE IN ATHENS LAUGH."

00:42:53.100 --> 00:43:00.564
 "IS THAT IT?"
 "FAREWELL AEGEUS."

00:43:00.600 --> 00:43:06.100
 "MAY THE GODS"
 "COMFORT YOU, MEDEA."

00:43:06.132 --> 00:43:09.232
 "FAREWELL,"
 "LADIES OF CORINTH."

00:43:09.264 --> 00:43:14.564
 "FAIR BE THE GALE BEHIND YOU,"
 "SIR, AND THE WAY AHEAD."

00:43:14.600 --> 00:43:19.064
 "WHAT IS SHE PLOTTING"
 "IN HER DEEP MIND?"

00:43:19.100 --> 00:43:22.432
 "SHE IS JUGGLING"
 "WITH DEATH AND LIFE"

00:43:22.464 --> 00:43:26.100
 "LIKE A JUGGLER WITH A BLACK"
 "BALL AND A WHITE BALL."

00:43:26.132 --> 00:43:33.400
 "OH GOD, PROTECTOR OF EXILES,"
 "LORD OF THE HOLY SKY, LEAD US TO"

00:43:33.432 --> 00:43:39.500
 "THE HIGH ROCK THAT ATHENA LOVES,"
 "AND THE OLIVE GARLAND OF ATHENS."

00:43:39.532 --> 00:43:44.132
 "ATHENS IS BEAUTIFUL"
 "AS A LAMP ON A ROCK."

00:43:44.164 --> 00:43:47.032
 "THE PEOPLE OF ATHENS"
 "FAVORED THROUGH THE AGES,"

00:43:47.064 --> 00:43:50.064
 "WALK WITH GRACE THROUGH"
 "THE SPARKLING AIR,"

00:43:50.100 --> 00:43:53.364
 "THEIR SOULS NOURISHED BY"
 "KNOWLEDGE AND WISDOM."

00:43:53.400 --> 00:43:56.464
 "HOW CAN SUCH A"
 "PEOPLE OFFER SHELTER"

00:43:56.500 --> 00:44:01.164
 "TO A WOMAN SO FILLED"
 "WITH HATRED AND MURDER?"

00:44:01.200 --> 00:44:03.532
 "HOW CAN ONE"
 "WISH TO DIE?"

00:44:03.564 --> 00:44:06.132
 "HOW CAN THAT WOMAN"
 "BE DROWNED IN SORROW"

00:44:06.164 --> 00:44:08.500
 "AND BEWILDERED"
 "WITH HATRED?"

00:44:08.532 --> 00:44:11.364
 "FOR ONLY TO BE ALIVE AND TO"
 "SEE THE LIGHT IS BEAUTIFUL."

00:44:11.400 --> 00:44:14.400
 "HUSH."

00:44:14.432 --> 00:44:17.600
 "AS YOU SAY."

00:44:17.632 --> 00:44:22.800
 "WHAT A MARVELOUS PRIVILEGE"
 "IT IS MERELY TO BE ALIVE."

00:44:22.832 --> 00:44:26.332
 "AND HOW FOOLISH IT WOULD BE"
 "TO SPEND THE ONE DAY OF LIFE"

00:44:26.364 --> 00:44:29.632
 "THAT REMAINS TO ME -"
 "AT LEAST IN CORINTH"

00:44:29.664 --> 00:44:34.232
 "- THIS TAG END OF ONE DAY"
 "ON TEARS AND HATRED."

00:44:34.264 --> 00:44:38.900
 "RATHER I SHOULD REJOICE,"
 "AND SING, AND GIVE GIFTS;"

00:44:38.932 --> 00:44:43.964
 "THEY SAY GOLD WILL BUY"
 "ANYTHING; EVEN FRIENDSHIP,"

00:44:44.000 --> 00:44:49.800
 "EVEN LOVE: AT LEAST IN GREECE,"
 "AMONG YOU CIVILIZED PEOPLE,"

00:44:49.832 --> 00:44:52.864
 "YOU REASONABLE AND"
 "CIVILIZED HELLENES."

00:44:52.900 --> 00:44:55.432
 "I STILL HAVE TWO OR THREE"
 "OF THE TREASURES THAT"

00:44:55.464 --> 00:45:00.100
 "I BROUGHT FROM HOME,"
 "THINGS OF PURE PRECIOUS GOLD"

00:45:00.132 --> 00:45:05.900
 "WHICH A GOD GAVE TO"
 "THE KINGS, MY ANCESTORS."

00:45:05.932 --> 00:45:10.732
 "IS IT LATE? IT SEEMS TO ME"
 "THAT THE LIGHT DARKENS."

00:45:10.764 --> 00:45:12.800
 "IS IT EVENING?"

00:45:12.832 --> 00:45:15.832
 "NO, NO, A CLOUD."

00:45:15.864 --> 00:45:20.300
 "I HOPE FOR THUNDER:"
 "LET THE SKY RAGE:"

00:45:20.332 --> 00:45:23.100
 "MY GIFTS WILL"
 "SHINE THE BRIGHTER."

00:45:23.132 --> 00:45:29.832
 "LISTEN, OLD WOMAN: I WANT YOU"
 "TO GO TO JASON AND TELL HIM,"

00:45:29.864 --> 00:45:33.900
 "TELL HIM...."

00:45:33.932 --> 00:45:37.864
 "TELL HIM I AM SICK OF"
 "HATING AND WEARY OF EVIL;"

00:45:37.900 --> 00:45:41.500
 "I WISH FOR PEACE. I WISH"
 "TO SEND PRECIOUS GIFTS"

00:45:41.532 --> 00:45:44.300
 "TO THAT PALE GIRL"
 "WITH THE YELLOW HAIR"

00:45:44.332 --> 00:45:47.064
 "WHOM HE HAS MARRIED: TELL"
 "HIM TO COME AND TAKE THEM,"

00:45:47.100 --> 00:45:50.264
 "AND TO KISS HIS BOYS"
 "BEFORE WE GO INTO EXILE."

00:45:50.300 --> 00:45:54.000
 "TELL HIM TO"
 "COME SPEEDILY."

00:45:54.032 --> 00:45:58.532
 "NOW GO,"
 "GO AND FIND HIM."

00:46:04.400 --> 00:46:14.264
 "OH, I'LL GO..."

00:46:14.300 --> 00:46:23.664
 "BUT I AM TERRIFIED."
 "I DO NOT KNOW."

00:46:23.700 --> 00:46:29.264
 "I AM TERRIFIED."

00:46:29.300 --> 00:46:39.932
 "PRAY TO THE GODS, WOMEN, TO KEEP"
 "EVIL BIRDS FROM OUR HEARTS!"

00:47:14.032 --> 00:47:18.100
 "THESE ARE THE GIFTS I AM"
 "SENDING TO THE YOUNG BRIDE:"

00:47:18.132 --> 00:47:21.500
 "THE GOD OF THE SUN GAVE"
 "THEM TO MY FATHER'S FATHER,"

00:47:21.532 --> 00:47:24.464
 "AND I HAVE KEPT"
 "THEM IN THE DEEP CHEST"

00:47:24.500 --> 00:47:30.364
 "FOR SOME HIGH OCCASION:"
 "WHICH HAS NOW COME."

00:47:30.400 --> 00:47:35.600
 "I HAVE GREAT JOY IN GIVING THESE"
 "JEWELS TO CREON'S DAUGHTER,"

00:47:35.632 --> 00:47:38.664
 "FOR THE GLORY OF LIFE"
 "CONSISTS IN BEING GENEROUS"

00:47:38.700 --> 00:47:43.200
 "TO ONE'S FRIENDS, AND"
 "MERCILESS TO ONE'S ENEMIES."

00:47:43.232 --> 00:47:46.532
 "YOU KNOW WHAT A FRIEND"
 "SHE HAS BEEN TO ME."

00:47:46.564 --> 00:47:49.832
 "ALL CORINTH KNOWS."
 "THE SLAVES TALK OF IT."

00:47:49.864 --> 00:47:55.664
 "THE OLD STONES IN THE WALLS"
 "HAVE WATCHED AND LAUGHED."

00:47:55.700 --> 00:48:00.200
 "SEE, IT IS"
 "ALMOST ALIVE."

00:48:00.232 --> 00:48:05.064
 "GOLD IS A LIVING THING:"
 "SUCH PURE GOLD."

00:48:05.100 --> 00:48:12.464
 "BUT WHEN HER BODY HAS"
 "WARMED IT, HOW IT WILL SHINE."

00:48:17.164 --> 00:48:19.264
 "IT IS INTOLERABLE"
 "TO SIT AND WAIT."

00:48:19.300 --> 00:48:21.732
 "YOU'RE SURE HE'S"
 "COMING? YOU'RE SURE?"

00:48:21.764 --> 00:48:23.800
 "HE SAID HE WOULD."

00:48:23.832 --> 00:48:25.664
 "LET HIM MAKE"
 "HASTE THEN."

00:48:25.700 --> 00:48:28.164
 "FRIGHTENING IRRATIONAL"
 "THINGS HAVE HAPPENED LATELY;"

00:48:28.200 --> 00:48:30.700
 "THE FACE OF NATURE IS"
 "FLAWED WITH OMENS."

00:48:30.732 --> 00:48:33.832
 "YESTERDAY EVENING A SLAVE"
 "CAME UP TO THE HARBOR-GATE"

00:48:33.864 --> 00:48:37.100
 "CARRYING A BASKET OF NEW-CAUGHT"
 "FISH: ONE OF THE FISH TOOK FIRE"

00:48:37.132 --> 00:48:40.064
 "AND BURNED IN THE WET"
 "BASKET WITH A HIGH FLAME:"

00:48:40.100 --> 00:48:42.632
 "THE THING WAS WITNESSED"
 "BY MANY PERSONS."

00:48:42.664 --> 00:48:44.400
 "AND A BLACK"
 "LEOPARD WAS SEEN"

00:48:44.432 --> 00:48:46.364
 "GLIDING THROUGH"
 "THE MARKET PLACE."

00:48:46.400 --> 00:48:49.032
 "YOU HAVEN'T TOLD ME YET: DO YOU"
 "NOT THINK CREON'S DAUGHTER"

00:48:49.064 --> 00:48:51.364
 "WILL BE GLAD"
 "OF THOSE GIFTS?"

00:48:51.400 --> 00:48:55.332
 "OH, MEDEA, TOO MUCH WEALTH"
 "IS SOMETIMES DREADFUL."

00:48:55.364 --> 00:48:57.700
 "SHE'LL BE GLAD,"
 "HOWEVER."

00:48:57.732 --> 00:49:01.964
 "SHE'LL TAKE THEM AND PUT"
 "THEM ON, SHE'LL WEAR THEM,"

00:49:02.000 --> 00:49:08.532
 "SHE'LL STRUT IN THEM."
 "SHE'LL PEACOCK IN THEM."

00:49:08.564 --> 00:49:12.332
 "I SEE HIM"
 "COMING NOW."

00:49:12.364 --> 00:49:16.864
 "THE WHOLE PALACE"
 "WILL ADMIRE HER."

00:49:16.900 --> 00:49:23.632
 "STAND ASIDE FROM ME, WOMEN,"
 "WHILE I MAKE MY SICK PEACE."

00:49:32.200 --> 00:49:35.500
 "WELL, I HAVE COME."

00:49:35.532 --> 00:49:39.832
 "I TELL YOU PLAINLY, NOT FOR"
 "YOUR SAKE: THE CHILDREN'S."

00:49:39.864 --> 00:49:44.064
 "YOUR WOMAN TELLS ME"
 "YOU HAVE YOUR WITS AGAIN"

00:49:44.100 --> 00:49:47.964
 "AND ARE WILLING TO LOOK"
 "BEYOND YOUR OWN WOES."

00:49:48.000 --> 00:49:52.032
 "IT APPEARS"
 "DOUBTFUL."

00:49:52.064 --> 00:49:54.532
 "WHERE ARE"
 "THE BOYS?"

00:49:54.564 --> 00:49:58.600
 "I'VE MADE INQUIRY: I CAN FIND"
 "FOSTERAGE FOR THEM IN EPIDAURUS;"

00:49:58.632 --> 00:50:01.564
 "OR ANY OTHER OF SEVERAL CITIES"
 "THAT ARE CREON'S FRIENDS."

00:50:01.600 --> 00:50:03.732
 "I'LL VISIT THEM"
 "FROM TIME TO TIME,"

00:50:03.764 --> 00:50:05.832
 "AND SEE THAT"
 "THEY'RE WELL KEPT."

00:50:05.864 --> 00:50:08.964
 "YOU MEAN... TAKE"
 "THEM FROM ME!"

00:50:09.000 --> 00:50:13.100
 "BE CAREFUL, JASON. I"
 "AM NOT PATIENT YET."

00:50:13.132 --> 00:50:16.232
 "I AM THE ONE WHO LABORED"
 "IN PAIN TO BEAR THEM,"

00:50:16.264 --> 00:50:19.100
 "I CANNOT SMILE"
 "WHILE I LOSE THEM."

00:50:19.132 --> 00:50:24.064
 "BUT I AM LEARNING;"
 "I AM LEARNING."

00:50:24.100 --> 00:50:27.664
 "NO, JASON: I WILL NOT"
 "GIVE UP MY LITTLE ONES"

00:50:27.700 --> 00:50:30.432
 "TO THE COLD CARE"
 "OF STRANGERS."

00:50:30.464 --> 00:50:34.132
 "IT WILL BE FAR BETTER FOR THEM"
 "TO SHARE MY WANDERING OCEAN"

00:50:34.164 --> 00:50:37.664
 "OF BEGGARY AND BLEAK EXILE:"
 "THEY'LL STILL BE LOVED;"

00:50:37.700 --> 00:50:41.332
 "AND WHEN THE SKY RAGES I'LL HOLD"
 "THEM WARM AGAINST MY HEART."

00:50:41.364 --> 00:50:43.800
 "I LOVE THEM, JASON."

00:50:43.832 --> 00:50:50.464
 "ONLY IF YOU WOULD KEEP THEM AND"
 "CARE FOR THEM HERE IN CORINTH,"

00:50:50.500 --> 00:50:52.700
 "I MIGHT CONSENT."

00:50:52.732 --> 00:50:54.900
 "GLADLY, BUT"
 "THEY ARE EXILED."

00:50:54.932 --> 00:50:57.532
 "GLADLY I'D DO IT: BUT YOU"
 "UNDERSTAND THEY ARE EXILED,"

00:50:57.564 --> 00:50:59.200
 "AS YOU ARE."

00:50:59.232 --> 00:51:03.032
 "INNOCENT; FOR MY"
 "REBELLION. THAT'S BLACK!"

00:51:03.064 --> 00:51:08.732
 "FORGIVE ME,"
 "JASON, AS I DO YOU."

00:51:08.764 --> 00:51:16.000
 "WE HAVE HAD TOO MUCH WRATH,"
 "AND OUR ACTS ARE CLOSING ON US."

00:51:16.032 --> 00:51:18.664
 "ON ME I MEAN."

00:51:18.700 --> 00:51:23.564
 "RETRIBUTION IS FROM THE GODS,"
 "AND IT BREAKS OUR HEARTS:"

00:51:23.600 --> 00:51:32.300
 "BUT YOU FEEL NO GUILT, YOU FEAR"
 "NOTHING, NOTHING CAN TOUCH YOU."

00:51:32.332 --> 00:51:35.764
 "IT IS WONDERFUL TO STAND"
 "SERENE ABOVE THE FATES"

00:51:35.800 --> 00:51:37.832
 "WHILE"
 "EARTHLINGS WINCE."

00:51:37.864 --> 00:51:40.632
 "IF IT LASTS. IT"
 "DOESN'T ALWAYS LAST."

00:51:40.664 --> 00:51:43.800
 "DO YOU LOVE"
 "THEM, JASON?"

00:51:43.832 --> 00:51:51.032
 "CERTAINLY. THE CHILDREN?"
 "CERTAINLY! I AM THEIR FATHER."

00:51:51.064 --> 00:51:54.032
 "IF ANYTHING HAPPENED TO"
 "THEM, WOULD YOU BE GRIEVED?"

00:51:54.064 --> 00:51:56.464
 "NOTHING WILL HAPPEN TO"
 "THEM, MEDEA, WHILE IN MY CARE."

00:51:56.500 --> 00:51:58.400
 "REST YOUR MIND ON IT."

00:51:58.432 --> 00:52:02.032
 "YOU MUST PARDON ME: IT IS NOT"
 "POSSIBLE TO BE CERTAIN OF THAT."

00:52:02.064 --> 00:52:08.200
 "IF THEY WERE KILLED AND THEIR"
 "BLOOD RAN ON THE FLOOR OF THE"

00:52:08.232 --> 00:52:15.464
 "HOUSE OR DOWN THE DEEP EARTH"
 "- WOULD YOU BE GRIEVED?"

00:52:15.500 --> 00:52:17.764
 "YOU HAVE A SICK MIND."

00:52:17.800 --> 00:52:21.400
 "WHAT A WEAK THING A WOMAN"
 "IS, ALWAYS DREAMING OF EVIL."

00:52:21.432 --> 00:52:25.100
 "YES! AFTER I'D CUT THEIR"
 "KILLER INTO RED COLLOPS:"

00:52:25.132 --> 00:52:26.864
 "I'D BE GRIEVED."

00:52:26.900 --> 00:52:30.600
 "THAT IS TRUE: VENGEANCE"
 "MAKES GRIEF BEARABLE."

00:52:30.632 --> 00:52:34.400
 "AND KNOWING THAT -"
 "CREON'S DAUGHTER, YOUR WIFE,"

00:52:34.432 --> 00:52:37.500
 "NO DOUBT WILL BREED"
 "MANY OTHER BOYS."

00:52:37.532 --> 00:52:40.600
 "BUT IF SOMETHING SHOULD"
 "HAPPEN TO CREON'S DAUGHTER..."

00:52:40.632 --> 00:52:42.864
 "ENOUGH, MEDEA."
 "TOO MUCH. BE SILENT!"

00:52:42.900 --> 00:52:44.964
 "I AM TO CONCLUDE THAT"
 "YOU LOVE CREON'S DAUGHTER"

00:52:45.000 --> 00:52:46.800
 "MORE THAN YOUR SONS."

00:52:46.832 --> 00:52:48.864
 "THEY'LL HAVE TO TAKE THE"
 "SAD JOURNEY WITH ME."

00:52:48.900 --> 00:52:53.500
 "TELL THE BOYS TO COME OUT"
 "AND BID THEIR FATHER FAREWELL."

00:52:53.532 --> 00:52:57.000
 "I COULD TAKE THEM FROM"
 "YOU BY FORCE, MEDEA."

00:52:57.032 --> 00:53:01.932
 "TRY IT, YOU...!"

00:53:01.964 --> 00:53:06.132
 "COME, JASON, LET'S"
 "BE FRIENDS AT LAST!"

00:53:06.164 --> 00:53:08.400
 "I KNOW YOU"
 "LOVE THEM."

00:53:08.432 --> 00:53:12.500
 "IF THEY COULD STAY HERE IN"
 "CORINTH I'D BE CONTENT."

00:53:12.532 --> 00:53:14.764
 "I ASKED IT, AND"
 "HE REFUSED IT."

00:53:14.800 --> 00:53:21.732
 "YOU ASKED HIM TO TAKE"
 "MY CHILDREN FROM ME!"

00:53:21.764 --> 00:53:26.764
 "I AM QUITE PATIENT"
 "NOW; I HAVE LEARNED."

00:53:26.800 --> 00:53:31.932
 "COME, BOYS, COME:"
 "SPEAK TO YOUR FATHER."

00:53:35.232 --> 00:53:38.932
 "NO, NO, WE'RE"
 "FRIENDS AGAIN."

00:53:38.964 --> 00:53:41.500
 "WE'RE NOT"
 "ANGRY ANYMORE."

00:53:41.532 --> 00:53:43.964
 "BIG BOYS,"
 "TALL FELLOWS,"

00:53:44.000 --> 00:53:46.200
 "WHY YOU'VE GROWN"
 "UP SINCE I SAW YOU."

00:53:46.232 --> 00:53:49.764
 "SMILE FOR HIM, CHILDREN."
 "GIVE HIM YOUR HANDS."

00:53:49.800 --> 00:53:52.964
 "I THINK HE'S AFRAID"
 "OF YOUR HELMET, SIR."

00:54:01.764 --> 00:54:08.932
 "MY SONS! MY SONS!"

00:54:08.964 --> 00:54:13.832
 "I'LL TEACH YOU NOT"
 "TO FEAR HELMETS."

00:54:13.864 --> 00:54:18.532
 "THE ENEMY WILL RUN FROM YOURS"
 "WHEN YOU GROW UP TO SIZE."

00:54:18.564 --> 00:54:23.964
 "AND IN TIME YOU'LL BOTH"
 "BE LEADERS OF CORINTH."

00:54:24.000 --> 00:54:27.900
 "YOU, MY CAPTAIN."

00:54:27.932 --> 00:54:30.564
 "DON'T GIVE THEM"
 "TO HIM, MEDEA."

00:54:30.600 --> 00:54:33.500
 "IF YOU DO, IT WILL"
 "ACHE FOREVER."

00:54:33.532 --> 00:54:37.064
 "YOU HAVE REFUGE: TAKE THEM"
 "THERE. ATHENS IS BEAUTIFUL."

00:54:37.100 --> 00:54:38.564
 "SILENT!"

00:54:38.600 --> 00:54:43.632
 "LOOK AT HIM: HE"
 "LOVES THEM, AH?"

00:54:43.664 --> 00:54:47.100
 "THEREFORE HIS DEAR CHILDREN"
 "ARE NOT GOING TO THAT CITY"

00:54:47.132 --> 00:54:49.200
 "BUT A DARKER CITY, WHERE"
 "NO GAMES ARE PLAYED,"

00:54:49.232 --> 00:54:51.600
 "NO MUSIC IS HEARD."

00:54:51.632 --> 00:54:53.700
 "WATCH AND SEE."

00:54:53.732 --> 00:54:56.500
 "WATCH THIS MAN, WOMEN:"
 "HE IS GOING TO WEEP."

00:54:56.532 --> 00:54:59.200
 "I THINK HE IS GOING TO"
 "WEEP BLOOD AND QUITE SOON"

00:54:59.232 --> 00:55:01.732
 "AND MUCH MORE"
 "THAN I HAVE WEPT."

00:55:01.764 --> 00:55:04.400
 "WATCH AND"
 "KEEP SILENCE."

00:55:04.432 --> 00:55:10.800
 "JASON, ARE THE BOYS"
 "VERY DEAR TO YOU?"

00:55:10.832 --> 00:55:14.200
 "I THINK I AM SATISFIED"
 "THAT YOU LOVE THEM."

00:55:14.232 --> 00:55:17.464
 "THESE TWO"
 "YOUNG HEROES...."

00:55:17.500 --> 00:55:22.332
 "GOD'S HAND, MEDEA, WHAT"
 "IS IT? WHAT'S THE MATTER?"

00:55:22.364 --> 00:55:33.064
 "NOTHING. IT IS HARD"
 "TO LET THEM GO."

00:55:33.100 --> 00:55:40.132
 "THIS I HAVE THOUGHT OF:"
 "YOU WILL TAKE THEM TO"

00:55:40.164 --> 00:55:45.200
 "CREON'S DAUGHTER, YOUR WIFE,"
 "AND MAKE THEM KNEEL TO HER"

00:55:45.232 --> 00:55:49.564
 "AND ASK HER TO ASK HER FATHER TO"
 "LET THEM STAY HERE IN CORINTH."

00:55:49.600 --> 00:55:52.564
 "AND I'LL PUT GIFTS"
 "IN THEIR HANDS."

00:55:52.600 --> 00:55:56.632
 "PEOPLE SAY THAT GIFTS WILL"
 "PERSUADE EVEN THE GODS."

00:55:56.664 --> 00:56:01.664
 "IS IT WELL THOUGHT OF?"
 "WILL SHE LISTEN TO US?"

00:56:01.700 --> 00:56:06.000
 "WHY, YES IF I ASK IT."
 "SHE'D DENY ME NOTHING."

00:56:06.032 --> 00:56:09.964
 "AND I THINK YOU'RE"
 "RIGHT, SHE CAN RULE CREON."

00:56:10.000 --> 00:56:13.364
 "BRING ME THOSE"
 "GOLD THINGS."

00:56:13.400 --> 00:56:20.200
 "DEAR ONES, BRAVE"
 "LITTLE FALCONS,"

00:56:20.232 --> 00:56:23.264
 "LITTLE PAWNS"
 "OF MY AGONY..."

00:56:23.300 --> 00:56:28.732
 "GO ASK THAT PROUD BREASTLESS"
 "GIRL OF HER BITTER CHARITY"

00:56:28.764 --> 00:56:32.700
 "WHETHER SHE WILL LET YOU NEST"
 "HERE UNTIL YOUR WINGS FLEDGE,"

00:56:32.732 --> 00:56:37.200
 "WHILE FAR YOUR MOTHER"
 "FLIES THE DARK STORM."

00:56:37.232 --> 00:56:42.064
 "I'M SORRY FOR YOU,"
 "MEDEA. PARTING IS HARD."

00:56:42.100 --> 00:56:44.964
 "I CAN BEAR IT."

00:56:45.000 --> 00:56:49.264
 "AND WORSE TOO."

00:56:49.300 --> 00:56:55.832
 "DON'T TOUCH THE GOLD,"
 "OR IT MIGHT TARNISH."

00:56:55.864 --> 00:56:58.164
 "WHY, THESE ARE A"
 "KING'S TREASURES."

00:56:58.200 --> 00:57:00.064
 "YOU SHOULDN'T,"
 "MEDEA: IT'S TOO MUCH."

00:57:00.100 --> 00:57:02.600
 "CREON'S HOUSE HAS"
 "ENOUGH GOLD OF ITS OWN."

00:57:02.632 --> 00:57:04.764
 "OH, IF SHE'LL"
 "WEAR THEM."

00:57:04.800 --> 00:57:07.700
 "WHAT SHOULD I WANT WITH"
 "WOVEN GOLDEN VANITIES?"

00:57:07.732 --> 00:57:09.432
 "BLACK IS MY WEAR."

00:57:09.464 --> 00:57:13.264
 "THE WOMAN OUGHT TO BE VERY"
 "HAPPY WITH SUCH JEWELS"

00:57:13.300 --> 00:57:16.600
 "- AND SUCH A HUSBAND, AH?"

00:57:16.632 --> 00:57:22.164
 "HER SUN IS RISING, MINE GOING"
 "DOWN: I HOPE TO A RED SUNSET."

00:57:22.200 --> 00:57:25.632
 "GOLD IS TOO HEAVY A"
 "BURDEN FOR LITTLE HANDS."

00:57:25.664 --> 00:57:30.132
 "CARRY THEM, YOU, UNTIL"
 "YOU COME TO THE PALACE."

00:57:30.164 --> 00:57:33.632
 "FAREWELL, SWEET BOYS:"

00:57:33.664 --> 00:57:40.332
 "BRAVE LITTLE"
 "TRUDGING PILGRIMS"

00:57:40.364 --> 00:57:47.400
 "FROM THE BLACK WAVE"
 "TO THE WHITE DESERT."

00:57:53.432 --> 00:57:58.432
 "TAKE THE STUFF IN, BE SURE"
 "YOU LAY IT IN HER OWN HANDS."

00:57:58.464 --> 00:58:02.600
 "COME BACK AND TELL"
 "ME WHAT HAPPENS."

00:58:06.700 --> 00:58:11.032
 "TELL ME"
 "WHAT HAPPENS."

00:58:17.164 --> 00:58:21.064
 "REJOICE, WOMEN."
 "THE GIFTS ARE GIVEN."

00:58:21.100 --> 00:58:23.232
 "THE BAIT IS LAID."

00:58:23.264 --> 00:58:26.300
 "THE GODS ROLL THEIR GREAT"
 "EYES OVER CREON'S HOUSE"

00:58:26.332 --> 00:58:30.364
 "AND QUIETLY SMILE: FOR NO RAT"
 "NOR CONY WOULD CREEP INTO"

00:58:30.400 --> 00:58:35.564
 "THE OPEN UNDISGUISED TRAPS THAT"
 "TAKE THE PROUD RACE OF MAN."

00:58:35.600 --> 00:58:41.064
 "THAT ROBE OF BRIGHT-FLOWING"
 "GOLD, THAT BRIDE-VEIL,"

00:58:41.100 --> 00:58:46.764
 "THAT FISH-NET TO CATCH A"
 "YOUNG SLENDER SALMON -"

00:58:46.800 --> 00:58:52.000
 "NOT MUTE, SHE'LL SING: HER"
 "DELICATE BODY WRITHES IN"

00:58:52.032 --> 00:58:55.164
 "THE MESHES, THE GOLDEN"
 "WREATH BINDS HER BRIGHT HEAD"

00:58:55.200 --> 00:58:59.800
 "WITH LIGHT: SHE'LL DANCE,"
 "SHE'LL SING LOUDLY:"

00:58:59.832 --> 00:59:05.100
 "WOULD I WERE THERE TO HEAR"
 "IT, THAT PROUD ONE HOWLING."

00:59:05.132 --> 00:59:14.500
 "LOOK, THE SUN'S OUT AGAIN,"
 "THE CLOUDS ARE GONE,"

00:59:14.532 --> 00:59:18.700
 "ALL'S GAY AND CLEAR."

00:59:18.732 --> 00:59:26.064
 "I WISH THE DEEP EARTH"
 "WOULD OPEN AND SWALLOW US"

00:59:26.100 --> 00:59:30.264
 "- BEFORE I DO"
 "WHAT COMES NEXT."

00:59:30.300 --> 00:59:33.800
 "I WISH ALL LIFE"
 "WOULD PERISH,"

00:59:33.832 --> 00:59:38.564
 "AND THE HOLY GODS"
 "IN HIGH HEAVEN DIE,"

00:59:38.600 --> 00:59:44.100
 "BEFORE MY LITTLE ONES"
 "COME HOME TO MY HANDS."

00:59:44.132 --> 00:59:47.800
 "IT WOULD BE BETTER FOR YOU,"
 "MEDEA, IF THE EARTH DID OPEN"

00:59:47.832 --> 00:59:51.200
 "HER JAWS AND TAKE YOU"
 "DOWN INTO DARKNESS."

00:59:51.232 --> 00:59:54.032
 "BUT ONE THING YOU WILL"
 "NOT DO, FOR YOU CANNOT,"

00:59:54.064 --> 00:59:57.132
 "YOU WILL NOT HURT"
 "YOUR OWN CHILDREN."

00:59:57.164 --> 01:00:00.832
 "NO BLOOD-LAPPING BEAST OF THE"
 "FIELD, SHE-BEAR NOR LIONESS,"

01:00:00.864 --> 01:00:06.800
 "NOR THE LEAN WOLF-BITCH,"
 "HURTS HER OWN TENDER WHELPS!"

01:00:06.832 --> 01:00:09.664
 "HOW COULD THAT GIRL'S"
 "DEATH SLAKE ME?"

01:00:09.700 --> 01:00:11.532
 "I AM SICK"
 "WITH TERROR."

01:00:11.564 --> 01:00:13.700
 "I'LL RUN TO THE PALACE,"
 "I'LL WARN THEM."

01:00:13.732 --> 01:00:15.300
 "WILL YOU?"

01:00:15.332 --> 01:00:20.464
 "GO. GO IF YOU WILL. GOD"
 "AND MY VENGEFUL GODDESS"

01:00:20.500 --> 01:00:22.664
 "ARE DOING THESE THINGS:"
 "YOU CANNOT PREVENT THEM,"

01:00:22.700 --> 01:00:25.164
 "BUT YOU COULD EASILY"
 "FALL INTO THE SAME FIRE."

01:00:25.200 --> 01:00:27.000
 "I AM AFRAID TO GO."

01:00:27.032 --> 01:00:28.732
 "YOU ARE WISE."

01:00:28.764 --> 01:00:31.464
 "ANYONE RUNNING BETWEEN"
 "ME AND MY JUSTICE"

01:00:31.500 --> 01:00:33.800
 "WILL REAP WHAT"
 "NO MAN WANTS."

01:00:33.832 --> 01:00:36.000
 "NOT JUSTICE: VENGEANCE."

01:00:36.032 --> 01:00:39.364
 "YOU HAVE SUFFERED EVIL,"
 "YOU WISH TO INFLICT EVIL."

01:00:39.400 --> 01:00:43.132
 "I DO ACCORDING TO NATURE,"
 "WHAT I HAVE TO DO."

01:00:43.164 --> 01:00:45.832
 "I DREAMED THAT SOMEONE"
 "GAVE GOOD FOR EVIL,"

01:00:45.864 --> 01:00:47.900
 "AND THE WORLD"
 "WAS AMAZED."

01:00:47.932 --> 01:00:51.700
 "ONLY A COWARD OR A MADMAN"
 "GIVES GOOD FOR EVIL..."

01:00:51.732 --> 01:00:58.100
 "DID YOU HEAR A THIN MUSIC"
 "LIKE A GIRL SCREAMING?"

01:00:58.132 --> 01:01:01.964
 "OR DID I PERHAPS"
 "IMAGINE IT?"

01:01:02.000 --> 01:01:06.000
 "HARK, IT IS MUSIC."

01:01:06.032 --> 01:01:09.232
 "LET ME GO, MEDEA! I'LL BE"
 "MUTE, I'LL SPEAK TO NO ONE."

01:01:09.264 --> 01:01:11.932
 "I CANNOT BEAR. LET"
 "ME GO TO MY HOUSE!"

01:01:11.964 --> 01:01:14.132
 "YOU WILL STAY HERE,"
 "AND WATCH THE END."

01:01:14.164 --> 01:01:16.232
 "YOU WILL BE QUIET,"
 "YOU WOMEN."

01:01:16.264 --> 01:01:18.332
 "YOU CAME TO SEE HOW"
 "THE BARBARIAN WOMAN"

01:01:18.364 --> 01:01:21.264
 "ENDURES BETRAYAL:"
 "WATCH AND YOU'LL KNOW."

01:01:21.300 --> 01:01:25.400
 "BLOOD IS THE SEED OF BLOOD,"
 "HUNDREDFOLD THE HARVEST,"

01:01:25.432 --> 01:01:29.564
 "THE GLEANERS THAT FOLLOW IT,"
 "THEIR FEET ARE CRIMSON."

01:01:35.432 --> 01:01:37.300
 "THE DEMON COMES"
 "THROUGH THE LOCKED DOOR"

01:01:37.332 --> 01:01:39.832
 "AND STRANGLES"
 "THE CHILD."

01:01:39.864 --> 01:01:42.564
 "SEE THE WHIRLWIND HANGING"
 "FROM THE BLACK SKY"

01:01:42.600 --> 01:01:44.900
 "LIKE A TWISTED ROPE,"
 "LIKE AN ERECT SERPENT,"

01:01:44.932 --> 01:01:47.064
 "ITS TAIL TEARS"
 "THE EARTH,"

01:01:47.100 --> 01:01:50.400
 "IT IS BRAIDED OF DUST AND"
 "LIGHTNING, WHO WILL FLY IN IT?"

01:01:50.432 --> 01:01:54.000
 "LET ME HIDE MYSELF FROM"
 "THESE NIGHT-SHORING PILLARS"

01:01:54.032 --> 01:02:00.364
 "AND THE DARK DOOR!"

01:02:00.400 --> 01:02:05.832
 "HAVE PATIENCE,"
 "WOMEN. BE QUIET."

01:02:05.864 --> 01:02:09.400
 "I AM QUITE SURE"
 "SOMETHING HAS HAPPENED;"

01:02:09.432 --> 01:02:13.500
 "PRESENTLY SOMEONE"
 "WILL BRING US NEWS."

01:02:13.532 --> 01:02:16.900
 "LOOK! THE CHILDREN"
 "ARE COMING."

01:02:16.932 --> 01:02:20.764
 "THEY HAVE BRIGHT THINGS IN THEIR"
 "HANDS: THEIR FACES ARE CLEAR"

01:02:20.800 --> 01:02:27.064
 "AND JOYOUS: WAS ALL THAT"
 "FEAR A DREAM, A DREAM?"

01:02:27.100 --> 01:02:30.464
 "REJOICE, MEDEA, I"
 "BRING GOOD NEWS."

01:02:30.500 --> 01:02:34.532
 "THE PRINCESS GRACIOUSLY RECEIVED"
 "YOUR PRESENTS AND SMILED:"

01:02:34.564 --> 01:02:36.532
 "IT IS PEACE"
 "BETWEEN YOU."

01:02:36.564 --> 01:02:40.564
 "SHE HAS WELCOMED THE LITTLE"
 "BOYS, THEY ARE SAFE FROM EXILE."

01:02:40.600 --> 01:02:43.964
 "AT FIRST SHE LOOKED ANGRILY"
 "AT THEM AND TURNED AWAY,"

01:02:44.000 --> 01:02:47.064
 "BUT JASON SAID "DON'T"
 "BE ANGRY AT YOUR FRIENDS."

01:02:47.100 --> 01:02:49.832
 "YOU OUGHT TO LOVE"
 "THOSE WHOM I LOVE."

01:02:49.864 --> 01:02:52.600
 "LOOK WHAT THEY'VE"
 "BROUGHT YOU, DEAR"."

01:02:52.632 --> 01:02:56.800
 "AND SHE LOOKED AND SAW IN THE"
 "DARK BOXES THE BRILLIANT GOLD:"

01:02:56.832 --> 01:02:59.732
 "SHE SMILED THEN,"
 "AND MARVELED AT IT."

01:02:59.764 --> 01:03:05.064
 "AND AFTERWARD SHE CARESSED"
 "THE CHILDREN; SHE EVEN SAID"

01:03:05.100 --> 01:03:10.464
 "THAT THIS LITTLE ONE'S HAIR"
 "WAS LIKE FINE-SPUN SILK."

01:03:10.500 --> 01:03:14.832
 "THEN JASON GAVE THEM THESE"
 "TOYS AND WE CAME AWAY."

01:03:14.864 --> 01:03:17.464
 "YES. IF THIS WERE ALL..."

01:03:17.500 --> 01:03:21.000
 "IF THIS WERE ALL, OLD MAN, I'D"
 "HAVE YOUR BONY LOINS BEATEN"

01:03:21.032 --> 01:03:23.400
 "TO A BLOOD-FROTH FOR THE"
 "GOOD NEWS YOU BRING."

01:03:23.432 --> 01:03:26.764
 "THERE'S MORE, HOWEVER."
 "IT WILL SOON COME."

01:03:28.464 --> 01:03:30.664
 "OH! TAKE THEM"
 "AWAY FROM ME!"

01:03:30.700 --> 01:03:33.464
 "I CANNOT BEAR,"
 "I CANNOT BEAR."

01:03:33.500 --> 01:03:35.500
 "CHILDREN, COME QUICKLY."

01:03:35.532 --> 01:03:38.300
 "IF THERE IS ANY MERCY OR"
 "FORBEARANCE IN HEAVEN"

01:03:38.332 --> 01:03:41.064
 "LET IT REACH DOWN TO"
 "TOUCH THAT DARK MIND"

01:03:41.100 --> 01:03:43.864
 "AND SAVE IT FROM"
 "WHAT IT DREAMS."

01:03:43.900 --> 01:03:45.432
 "WHERE IS MEDEA?"

01:03:45.464 --> 01:03:47.532
 "WHAT HAS HAPPENED?"
 "WHAT HORROR DRIVES YOU?"

01:03:47.564 --> 01:03:49.700
 "ARE SPEARS HUNTING"
 "BEHIND YOU?"

01:03:53.600 --> 01:03:55.732
 "FLEE FOR YOUR"
 "LIFE, MEDEA!"

01:03:55.764 --> 01:03:57.564
 "I AM JASON'S MAN, BUT"
 "YOU WERE GOOD TO ME"

01:03:57.600 --> 01:03:59.632
 "WHILE I WAS HERE"
 "IN THE HOUSE."

01:03:59.664 --> 01:04:03.464
 "CAN YOU HEAR ME?"
 "ESCAPE, MEDEA!"

01:04:03.500 --> 01:04:05.532
 "I HEAR YOU."

01:04:05.564 --> 01:04:08.964
 "DRAW BREATH; SAY QUIETLY"
 "WHAT YOU HAVE SEEN."

01:04:09.000 --> 01:04:15.164
 "MY EARS RING WITH THE CRYING,"
 "MY EYES ARE SCALDED."

01:04:15.200 --> 01:04:17.832
 "SHE PUT ON THE"
 "GOLD GARMENTS...."

01:04:17.864 --> 01:04:20.700
 "DID YOU DO IT, MEDEA?"

01:04:20.732 --> 01:04:22.932
 "SPEAK QUIETLY."

01:04:22.964 --> 01:04:26.064
 "YOU ARE AVENGED. YOU"
 "ARE HORRIBLY AVENGED."

01:04:26.100 --> 01:04:30.900
 "IT IS TOO MUCH. THE"
 "GODS WILL HATE YOU."

01:04:30.932 --> 01:04:33.764
 "THAT IS MY CARE. DID"
 "ANYONE DIE WITH HER?"

01:04:33.800 --> 01:04:35.700
 "CREON!"

01:04:35.732 --> 01:04:42.700
 "TELL ME ALL THAT YOU"
 "SAW. SPEAK SLOWLY."

01:04:42.732 --> 01:04:46.932
 "HE TRIED TO SAVE HER"
 "- HE DIED!"

01:04:46.964 --> 01:04:49.164
 "CORINTH IS MASTERLESS!"

01:04:49.200 --> 01:04:52.200
 "ALL'S IN AMAZED CONFUSION,"
 "AND SOME ARE LOOTING,"

01:04:52.232 --> 01:04:55.132
 "BUT THEY'LL AVENGE HIM."

01:04:55.164 --> 01:04:56.900
 "I'M GOING ON!"

01:04:56.932 --> 01:04:59.632
 "SOMEONE IS"
 "GOING TO DIE."

01:04:59.664 --> 01:05:04.532
 "HERE COMES"
 "MY WITNESS."

01:05:04.564 --> 01:05:08.732
 "I'VE HOBBLED AND"
 "RUN, AND FALLEN."

01:05:08.764 --> 01:05:11.532
 "CATCH YOUR BREATH;"
 "TAKE YOUR TIME."

01:05:11.564 --> 01:05:17.332
 "I WANT THE WHOLE TALE;"
 "EVERY GESTURE AND CRY."

01:05:17.364 --> 01:05:22.132
 "I'VE LABORED FOR THIS."

01:05:22.164 --> 01:05:24.432
 "DEATH IS"
 "TURNED LOOSE."

01:05:24.464 --> 01:05:29.132
 "PLEASE, NURSE; I'M"
 "VERY HAPPY. GO SLOWLY."

01:05:29.164 --> 01:05:32.732
 "TELL ME THESE THINGS IN"
 "ORDER FROM THE BEGINNING"

01:05:32.764 --> 01:05:35.800
 "AS WHEN YOU USED TO"
 "DRESS ME, WHEN I WAS LITTLE,"

01:05:35.832 --> 01:05:38.900
 "IN MY FATHER'S HOUSE:"
 "YOU USED TO SAY"

01:05:38.932 --> 01:05:46.364
 ""ONE THING AT A TIME; ONE"
 "THING AND THEN THE NEXT"."

01:05:46.400 --> 01:05:52.900
 "MY EYES ARE BLISTERED, MY"
 "THROAT'S LIKE A DRY STRAW."

01:05:52.932 --> 01:06:01.064
 "THERE WAS A LONG MIRROR ON THE"
 "WALL, AND WHEN HER EYES SAW IT,"

01:06:01.100 --> 01:06:09.032
 "THE CHILDREN HAD GONE, SHE"
 "PUT HER HANDS IN THE CASES"

01:06:09.064 --> 01:06:13.000
 "AND TOOK THOSE GOLD THINGS -"
 "AND I WATCHED, FOR I FEARED"

01:06:13.032 --> 01:06:18.700
 "SOMETHING MIGHT HAPPEN TO HER,"
 "BUT I NEVER THOUGHT SO HORRIBLY"

01:06:18.732 --> 01:06:23.900
 "- SHE PLACED ON HER LITTLE HEAD"
 "THE BRIGHT GOLDEN WREATH,"

01:06:23.932 --> 01:06:26.400
 "SHE GATHERED THE"
 "FLOWING GOLD ROBE"

01:06:26.432 --> 01:06:29.464
 "AROUND HER WHITE SHOULDERS"
 "AND SLENDER FLANKS,"

01:06:29.500 --> 01:06:33.200
 "AND GAZED AT THE GOLDEN"
 "GIRL IN THE METAL MIRROR,"

01:06:33.232 --> 01:06:36.664
 "GOING BACK AND FORTH"
 "ON TIPTOE ALMOST;"

01:06:36.700 --> 01:06:39.364
 "AND SWUNG HER"
 "LEG FROM THE HIP"

01:06:39.400 --> 01:06:44.600
 "TO SEE THE FLEXIBLE GOLD"
 "MOULDING THE THIGH."

01:06:44.632 --> 01:06:48.100
 "BUT SUDDENLY"
 "HORROR BEGAN."

01:06:48.132 --> 01:06:51.732
 "YOU ARE NOT SUFFERING. YOU"
 "SAW IT, YOU DID NOT FEEL IT."

01:06:51.764 --> 01:06:53.864
 "SPEAK PLAINLY."

01:06:53.900 --> 01:06:57.164
 "HER FACE WENT WHITE; SHE"
 "STAGGERED A FEW STEPS,"

01:06:57.200 --> 01:07:00.464
 "BENDING OVER, AND FELL INTO"
 "THE GREAT THRONE-CHAIR;"

01:07:00.500 --> 01:07:03.300
 "THEN A SERVING-WOMAN"
 "BEGAN TO CALL FOR WATER"

01:07:03.332 --> 01:07:05.332
 "THINKING SHE"
 "HAD FAINTED,"

01:07:05.364 --> 01:07:08.664
 "BUT SAW THE FOAM START ON HER"
 "LIPS, AND THE EYES ROLLING,"

01:07:08.700 --> 01:07:11.164
 "AND SCREAMED INSTEAD."

01:07:11.200 --> 01:07:13.964
 "THEN SOME OF THEM RAN AFTER"
 "JASON, OTHERS RAN TO FETCH"

01:07:14.000 --> 01:07:17.200
 "CREON: AND THAT DOOMED GIRL"
 "FRIGHTFULLY CRYING STARTED UP"

01:07:17.232 --> 01:07:20.764
 "FROM THE CHAIR; SHE RAN, SHE WAS"
 "LIKE A TORCH, AND THE GOLD CROWN"

01:07:20.800 --> 01:07:24.600
 "LIKE A COMET STREAMED FIRE;"
 "SHE TORE AT IT BUT IT CLUNG TO"

01:07:24.632 --> 01:07:28.100
 "HER HEAD; THE GOLDEN CLOAK WAS"
 "WHITE-HOT, FLAYING THE FLESH"

01:07:28.132 --> 01:07:31.864
 "FROM THE LIVING BONES; BLOOD"
 "MIXED WITH FIRE RAN DOWN,"

01:07:31.900 --> 01:07:35.864
 "SHE FELL, SHE BURNED"
 "ON THE FLOOR, WRITHING."

01:07:35.900 --> 01:07:40.964
 "THEN CREON CAME AND"
 "FLUNG HIMSELF ON HER,"

01:07:41.000 --> 01:07:45.864
 "HOPING TO CHOKE THAT RAGE OF"
 "FLAME, BUT IT RAN THROUGH HIM,"

01:07:45.900 --> 01:07:48.664
 "HIS OWN AGONY MADE HIM"
 "FORGET HIS DAUGHTER'S."

01:07:48.700 --> 01:07:51.664
 "THE FIRE STUCK TO THE FLESH,"
 "IT GLUED HIM TO HER;"

01:07:51.700 --> 01:07:56.500
 "HE TRIED TO STAND UP, HE"
 "TORE HER BODY AND HIS OWN."

01:07:56.532 --> 01:08:01.132
 "THE BURNT FLESH BROKE"
 "IN LUMPS FROM THE BONES."

01:08:01.164 --> 01:08:05.864
 "NO, NO, NO MORE!"
 "I HAVE FINISHED."

01:08:05.900 --> 01:08:12.532
 "THEY LIE THERE. EYELESS,"
 "DISFACED, UNTOUCHABLE;"

01:08:12.564 --> 01:08:19.432
 "MIDDENS OF SMOKING FLESH"
 "LACED WITH MOLTEN GOLD."

01:08:19.464 --> 01:08:25.032
 "NO! I HAVE FINISHED. I HAVE"
 "NO MORE. HAVE MERCY..."

01:08:25.064 --> 01:08:27.132
 "HAD THEY DIED WHEN"
 "YOU CAME AWAY?"

01:08:27.164 --> 01:08:29.100
 "NO, THE HARSH"
 "TIDES OF BREATH"

01:08:29.132 --> 01:08:32.664
 "STILL WHISTLED IN"
 "THEIR BLACK MOUTHS."

01:08:32.700 --> 01:08:35.564
 "NO ONE COULD"
 "TOUCH THEM."

01:08:35.600 --> 01:08:37.764
 "AND JASON?"

01:08:37.800 --> 01:08:48.300
 "JASON STOOD IN THEIR"
 "SMOKE, UNABLE, HELPLESS.."

01:08:48.332 --> 01:08:52.864
 "NO ONE COULD"
 "TOUCH THEM."

01:09:02.032 --> 01:09:05.300
 "YOU HAVE TOLD"
 "GOOD NEWS WELL."

01:09:05.332 --> 01:09:08.964
 "I'LL REWARD YOU."

01:09:09.000 --> 01:09:13.832
 "AS FOR THOSE PEOPLE,"
 "THEY WILL SOON DIE."

01:09:13.864 --> 01:09:17.732
 "THEIR WOES ARE"
 "OVER TOO SOON."

01:09:17.764 --> 01:09:27.532
 "MINE ARE NOT."
 "JASON'S ARE NOT."

01:09:32.900 --> 01:09:40.532
 "MY LITTLE FALCONS!"
 "LISTEN TO ME:"

01:09:40.564 --> 01:09:46.564
 "LAUGH AND BE GLAD: WE"
 "HAVE ACCOMPLISHED IT."

01:09:46.600 --> 01:09:50.064
 "OUR ENEMIES WERE"
 "GREAT AND POWERFUL,"

01:09:50.100 --> 01:09:54.832
 "THEY WERE FULL OF COLD PRIDE,"
 "THEY RULED ALL THIS COUNTRY:"

01:09:54.864 --> 01:09:57.132
 "THEY ARE DOWN"
 "IN THE ASHES"

01:09:57.164 --> 01:10:02.132
 "HOWLING IN THE ASHES,"
 "IN THEIR OWN ASHES."

01:10:02.164 --> 01:10:05.864
 "NO ONE HAS"
 "EVER INJURED ME"

01:10:05.900 --> 01:10:09.400
 "BUT SUFFERED MORE"
 "THAN I HAD SUFFERED."

01:10:09.432 --> 01:10:17.332
 "THEREFORE THIS FINAL SACRIFICE"
 "I INTENDED GLARES IN MY EYES"

01:10:17.364 --> 01:10:21.732
 "LIKE A LION ON A RIDGE."

01:10:21.764 --> 01:10:25.864
 "WE STILL HATE, YOU KNOW: A"
 "PERSON NEARER THAN THESE,"

01:10:25.900 --> 01:10:35.632
 "MORE VILE, MORE CONTEMPTIBLE,"
 "WHOM I... I CANNOT..."

01:10:35.664 --> 01:10:43.364
 "IF HE WERE MY OWN HANDS I"
 "WOULD CUT HIM OFF, OR MY EYES,"

01:10:43.400 --> 01:10:49.264
 "I WOULD GOUGE HIM OUT, BUT"
 "NOT YOU: THAT WAS MADNESS."

01:10:49.300 --> 01:10:55.064
 "SO JASON WILL BE ABLE TO SAY"
 ""I HAVE LOST MUCH, BUT NOT ALL:"

01:10:55.100 --> 01:11:00.832
 "I HAVE CHILDREN:"
 "MY SONS ARE WELL"."

01:11:00.864 --> 01:11:04.500
 "THAT TOO IS"
 "UNBEARABLE."

01:11:04.532 --> 01:11:12.464
 "I WANT HIM CRUSHED,"
 "BONELESS, CRAWLING."

01:11:12.500 --> 01:11:17.232
 "I HAVE NO CHOICE."

01:11:17.264 --> 01:11:19.464
 "YOU THERE!"

01:11:19.500 --> 01:11:24.932
 "YOU THOUGHT ME SOFT AND"
 "SUBMISSIVE LIKE A COMMON WOMAN,"

01:11:24.964 --> 01:11:28.364
 "WHO TAKES A BLOW AND CRIES"
 "A LITTLE AND WIPES HER FACE"

01:11:28.400 --> 01:11:31.232
 "AND RUNS ABOUT THE HOUSEWORK,"
 "LOVING HER MASTER?"

01:11:31.264 --> 01:11:33.832
 "I AM NOT"
 "SUCH A WOMAN."

01:11:33.864 --> 01:11:37.200
 "AWAKE, MEDEA! AWAKE"
 "FROM THE EVIL DREAM."

01:11:37.232 --> 01:11:39.200
 "CATCH UP YOUR"
 "CHILDREN AND FLEE."

01:11:39.232 --> 01:11:42.232
 "FARTHER THAN ATHENS, FARTHER"
 "THAN THRACE OR SPAIN,"

01:11:42.264 --> 01:11:44.532
 "FLEE TO THE"
 "WORLD'S END."

01:11:44.564 --> 01:11:46.964
 "FIRE AND DEATH HAVE"
 "DONE YOUR BIDDING,"

01:11:47.000 --> 01:11:51.000
 "ARE YOU NOT FED FULL OF"
 "EVIL? IS IT NOT ENOUGH?"

01:11:51.032 --> 01:11:55.064
 "NO. LOATHING"
 "IS ENDLESS."

01:11:55.100 --> 01:12:03.700
 "HATE IS A BOTTOMLESS CUP,"
 "I WILL POUR AND POUR."

01:12:03.732 --> 01:12:16.900
 "CHILDREN! OH MY LITTLE"
 "ONES. WHAT WAS I DREAMING?"

01:12:16.932 --> 01:12:22.132
 "MY BABES, MY OWN!"

01:12:22.164 --> 01:12:30.732
 "NEVER, NEVER, NEVER SHALL"
 "MY OWN BABES BE HURT."

01:12:30.764 --> 01:12:35.332
 "NOT IF EVERY WAR-HOUND AND"
 "SPEAR-SLAVE IN HEADLESS CORINTH"

01:12:35.364 --> 01:12:39.300
 "WERE ON THE TRACK."

01:12:39.332 --> 01:12:43.732
 "LOOK, THEIR SWEET LIPS ARE"
 "TREMBLING: LOOK, WOMEN,"

01:12:43.764 --> 01:12:49.100
 "THE LITTLE MOUTHS: I FRIGHTENED"
 "THEM WITH THOSE WILD WORDS:"

01:12:49.132 --> 01:12:55.800
 "THEY STOOD AND FACED"
 "ME, THEY NEVER FLINCHED."

01:12:55.832 --> 01:12:58.964
 "LOOK AT THEIR"
 "PROUD YOUNG EYES!"

01:12:59.000 --> 01:13:05.932
 "MY EAGLETS,"
 "MY GOLDEN ONES!"

01:13:05.964 --> 01:13:15.964
 "OH SWEET SMALL FACES LIKE"
 "THE PALE WILD ROSES THAT BLOOM"

01:13:16.000 --> 01:13:21.200
 "WHERE THE CLIFF BREAKS TOWARD"
 "THE BRILLIANT SEA: THE DELICATE"

01:13:21.232 --> 01:13:29.664
 "FOAM AND COLOR, THE DEAR, DEAR"
 "FRAGRANCE OF YOUR SWEET BREATH."

01:13:29.700 --> 01:13:34.232
 "MY LADY: MAKE HASTE! TAKE"
 "THEM AND FLEE AWAY FROM HERE!"

01:13:34.264 --> 01:13:36.964
 "SOMEONE WILL COME"
 "SOON. OH LISTEN TO ME."

01:13:37.000 --> 01:13:39.900
 "ALL CORINTH IS IN CONFUSION"
 "AND HEADLESS ANARCHY,"

01:13:39.932 --> 01:13:42.332
 "UNKINGED AND AMAZED"
 "AROUND THAT HORROR YOU MADE:"

01:13:42.364 --> 01:13:46.264
 "THEREFORE THEY LINGER: YET IN"
 "A MOMENT ITS AVENGERS COME!"

01:13:46.300 --> 01:13:50.200
 "I HAVE A SWORD IN THE"
 "HOUSE. I CAN DEFEND YOU."

01:13:50.232 --> 01:13:54.432
 "WOULD YOU SAY THAT THIS"
 "CHILD HAS JASON'S EYES?"

01:13:54.464 --> 01:13:59.600
 "THEY ARE HIS CUBS."
 "THEY HAVE HIS BLOOD."

01:13:59.632 --> 01:14:10.564
 "AS LONG AS THEY LIVE I"
 "SHALL BE MIXED WITH HIM."

01:14:10.600 --> 01:14:27.600
 "CHILDREN... IT IS EVENING."
 "SEE, EVENING HAS COME."

01:14:27.632 --> 01:14:30.500
 "COME, LITTLE ONES,"
 "INTO THE HOUSE."

01:14:30.532 --> 01:14:34.200
 "EVENING BRINGS"
 "ALL THINGS HOME."

01:14:34.232 --> 01:14:39.464
 "IT BRINGS THE BIRD TO THE BOUGH"
 "AND THE LAMB TO THE FOLD,"

01:14:39.500 --> 01:14:47.364
 "AND THE CHILD"
 "TO THE MOTHER."

01:14:47.400 --> 01:14:50.664
 "WE MUST NOT"
 "THINK TOO MUCH:"

01:14:50.700 --> 01:14:54.764
 "PEOPLE GO MAD IF"
 "THEY THINK TOO MUCH."

01:15:09.432 --> 01:15:18.664
 "NO! NO! NO!!!!"

01:15:18.700 --> 01:15:21.000
 "WHAT HAS HAPPENED?"

01:15:21.032 --> 01:15:23.200
 "THAT CROWN OF HORRORS."

01:15:23.232 --> 01:15:25.732
 "(CHILDREN SCREAMING)"

01:15:25.764 --> 01:15:28.600
 "MEDEA, NO!"

01:15:28.632 --> 01:15:32.200
 "PREVENT HER! SAVE THEM!"

01:15:32.232 --> 01:15:34.100
 "OPEN THE DOOR."

01:15:34.132 --> 01:15:37.564
 "A GOD IS HERE, MEDEA. HE"
 "CALLS TO YOU, HE FORBIDS YOU!"

01:15:37.600 --> 01:15:49.300
 "(FADING SCREAMS)"

01:15:49.332 --> 01:15:54.200
 "THERE IS NO HOPE"
 "IN HEAVEN OR EARTH."

01:15:54.232 --> 01:15:56.564
 "IT IS DONE."

01:15:56.600 --> 01:16:06.400
 "IT WAS DESTINED WHEN SHE"
 "WAS BORN, NOW IT IS DONE."

01:16:06.432 --> 01:16:09.032
 "WHO IS COMING?"

01:16:09.064 --> 01:16:11.564
 "SOMEONE IS"
 "RUNNING AT US!"

01:16:11.600 --> 01:16:15.132
 "THE ACCURSED"
 "MAN, JASON."

01:16:15.164 --> 01:16:17.900
 "HE HAS A SWORD!"

01:16:17.932 --> 01:16:23.164
 "I AM MORE AFRAID OF THE CLINGING"
 "CONTAGION OF HIS MISFORTUNES."

01:16:23.200 --> 01:16:28.264
 "A MAN THE GODS"
 "ARE DESTROYING."

01:16:28.300 --> 01:16:30.432
 "WHERE IS THAT"
 "MURDERESS?"

01:16:30.464 --> 01:16:33.332
 "HERE IN THE HOUSE"
 "OR HAS SHE FLED?"

01:16:33.364 --> 01:16:36.164
 "SHE'LL HAVE TO HIDE IN"
 "THE HEAVY METAL DARKNESS"

01:16:36.200 --> 01:16:40.500
 "AND CAVES OF THE EARTH - AND"
 "THERE I'LL CRAWL AND FIND HER."

01:16:46.132 --> 01:16:49.632
 "ARE YOU STRUCK DUMB?"
 "ARE YOU SHIELDING HER?"

01:16:49.664 --> 01:16:51.432
 "WHERE IS MEDEA?"

01:16:51.464 --> 01:16:53.364
 "YOU CAUSED"
 "THESE THINGS."

01:16:53.400 --> 01:16:55.800
 "SHE WAS FAITHFUL TO"
 "YOU AND YOU BROKE FAITH."

01:16:55.832 --> 01:16:57.764
 "HORROR IS HERE."

01:16:57.800 --> 01:17:01.100
 "UNCAUSED. THERE"
 "WAS NO REASON!"

01:17:01.132 --> 01:17:05.932
 "TELL ME AT LEAST WHETHER"
 "SHE TOOK MY SONS WITH HER?"

01:17:05.964 --> 01:17:08.532
 "CREON'S MEN WOULD KILL"
 "THEM FOR WHAT SHE HAS DONE:"

01:17:08.564 --> 01:17:11.200
 "I'D RATHER SAVE"
 "THEM THAN PUNISH HER."

01:17:11.232 --> 01:17:14.132
 "HELP ME IN THIS."

01:17:14.164 --> 01:17:18.800
 "(MOANING)"

01:17:18.832 --> 01:17:21.732
 "SO SHE HAS"
 "KILLED HERSELF."

01:17:21.764 --> 01:17:24.900
 "GOOD. SHE NEVER"
 "LACKED COURAGE."

01:17:24.932 --> 01:17:28.264
 "I'LL TAKE MY SONS TO"
 "THE FAR END OF THE EARTH,"

01:17:28.300 --> 01:17:31.564
 "AND NEVER SPEAK OF"
 "THESE THINGS AGAIN."

01:17:31.600 --> 01:17:36.064
 "OH, OH, OH..."

01:17:36.100 --> 01:17:39.632
 "IS SHE LYING"
 "IN THERE?"

01:17:39.664 --> 01:17:41.864
 "HONORABLE AT"
 "LEAST IN HER DEATH,"

01:17:41.900 --> 01:17:44.164
 "I MIGHT"
 "HAVE KNOWN IT."

01:17:44.200 --> 01:17:46.564
 "WELL, ANSWER ME!"

01:17:46.600 --> 01:17:49.864
 "DEATH IS THERE;"
 "DEATH IS HERE."

01:17:49.900 --> 01:17:55.500
 "BUT YOU ARE BOTH BLIND AND"
 "DEAF: HOW CAN I TELL YOU?"

01:17:55.532 --> 01:17:58.800
 "BUT THE CHILDREN"
 "ARE WELL?"

01:17:58.832 --> 01:18:07.064
 "I DO NOT KNOW WHETHER"
 "MEDEA LIVES OR IS DEAD."

01:18:13.964 --> 01:18:21.600
 "OPEN! OPEN THE"
 "DOOR! OPEN! OPEN!"

01:18:21.632 --> 01:18:29.532
 "WOMEN: I AM "
 "ALONE. HELP ME."

01:18:29.564 --> 01:18:33.832
 "HELP ME TO"
 "BREAK THE BOLT!"

01:18:33.864 --> 01:18:38.864
 "GO AND FIND HELP!"

01:18:47.732 --> 01:18:53.100
 "WHAT FEEBLE NIGHT-BIRD OVERCOME"
 "BY MISFORTUNE BEATS AT MY DOOR?"

01:18:53.132 --> 01:18:56.532
 "CAN THIS BE THAT"
 "GREAT ADVENTURER,"

01:18:56.564 --> 01:19:00.732
 "THE FAMOUS LORD OF THE SEAS"
 "AND DELIGHT OF WOMEN,"

01:19:00.764 --> 01:19:03.364
 "THE HEIR OF"
 "RICH CORINTH,"

01:19:03.400 --> 01:19:07.164
 "THIS CRYING DRUNKARD"
 "ON THE DARK DOORSTEP?"

01:19:07.200 --> 01:19:09.700
 "YET YOU'VE NOT"
 "HAD ENOUGH."

01:19:09.732 --> 01:19:13.232
 "YOU HAVE COME TO DRINK"
 "THE LAST BITTER DROPS."

01:19:13.264 --> 01:19:16.832
 "I'LL POUR THEM FOR YOU."

01:19:16.864 --> 01:19:20.300
 "WHAT'S THAT STAIN"
 "ON YOUR HAND?"

01:19:20.332 --> 01:19:24.464
 "THE WINE I WAS POURING"
 "FOR YOU SPILLED ON MY HAND."

01:19:24.500 --> 01:19:28.832
 "DEAR WERE THE LITTLE GRAPES"
 "THAT WERE CRUSHED TO MAKE IT;"

01:19:28.864 --> 01:19:31.900
 "DEAR WERE"
 "THE VINEYARDS."

01:19:31.932 --> 01:19:35.200
 "I CAME TO KILL YOU, MEDEA,"
 "LIKE A CAUGHT BEAST,"

01:19:35.232 --> 01:19:37.664
 "LIKE A"
 "CRAWLING VIPER."

01:19:37.700 --> 01:19:42.264
 "GIVE ME MY SONS, THAT I MAY"
 "SAVE THEM FROM CREON'S MEN,"

01:19:42.300 --> 01:19:44.400
 "I'LL GO QUIETLY AWAY."

01:19:44.432 --> 01:19:47.064
 "HUSH: THEY"
 "ARE SLEEPING."

01:19:47.100 --> 01:19:50.532
 "PERHAPS I WILL LET YOU LOOK AT"
 "THEM: YOU CANNOT HAVE THEM."

01:19:50.564 --> 01:19:54.300
 "BUT THE HOUR IS LATE, YOU OUGHT"
 "TO GO HOME TO THAT HIGH-BORN"

01:19:54.332 --> 01:19:58.364
 "BRIDE; THE NIGHT HAS FALLEN,"
 "SURELY SHE LONGS FOR YOU."

01:19:58.400 --> 01:20:02.400
 "SURELY HER FLESH IS NOT CRUSTED"
 "BLACK, NOR HER MOUTH A HORROR."

01:20:02.432 --> 01:20:05.464
 "SHE IS VERY YOUNG, BUT"
 "SURELY SHE WILL BE FRUITFUL."

01:20:05.500 --> 01:20:07.664
 "YOUR SWORD YOU"
 "WANT? THERE IT IS."

01:20:07.700 --> 01:20:10.564
 "NOT THAT STEP,"
 "THE NEXT LOWER."

01:20:10.600 --> 01:20:17.564
 "I'LL KILL YOU FIRST AND"
 "THEN I'LL FIND MY SONS."

01:20:17.600 --> 01:20:21.132
 "DO YOU SEE THE TWO FIRE-SNAKES"
 "THAT GUARD THIS DOOR?"

01:20:21.164 --> 01:20:23.264
 "ONE ON EACH SIDE:"
 "TWO SERPENTS."

01:20:23.300 --> 01:20:25.800
 "THEIR THROATS ARE"
 "SWOLLEN WITH POISON,"

01:20:25.832 --> 01:20:28.400
 "THEIR EYES ARE BURNING COALS"
 "AND THEIR TONGUES ARE FIRE."

01:20:28.432 --> 01:20:31.900
 "THEY ARE COILED READY TO"
 "STRIKE: IF YOU COME NEAR THEM,"

01:20:31.932 --> 01:20:34.964
 "THEY'LL MAKE YOU"
 "WHAT CREON IS."

01:20:35.000 --> 01:20:42.932
 "BUT STAND THERE VERY QUIETLY,"
 "I'LL LET YOU LOOK AT YOUR SONS."

01:20:42.964 --> 01:20:48.264
 "OPEN THE DOORS,"
 "THAT HE MAY SEE THEM."

01:21:07.000 --> 01:21:09.200
 "I KNEW IT."

01:21:09.232 --> 01:21:12.900
 "I KNEW IT BEFORE"
 "I SAW IT, I KNEW."

01:21:12.932 --> 01:21:16.664
 "NO WILD BEAST"
 "WOULD HAVE DONE IT."

01:21:16.700 --> 01:21:20.232
 "I HAVE DONE IT"
 "BECAUSE I LOATHED YOU"

01:21:20.264 --> 01:21:22.164
 "MORE THAN I"
 "LOVED THEM."

01:21:22.200 --> 01:21:24.364
 "I SHOULD HAVE KILLED"
 "YOU THE DAY I SAW YOU."

01:21:24.400 --> 01:21:28.800
 "I TORE MY OWN HEART AND"
 "LAUGHED: I WAS TEARING YOURS."

01:21:28.832 --> 01:21:31.300
 "WILL YOU LAUGH WHILE"
 "I STRANGLE YOU?"

01:21:31.332 --> 01:21:33.564
 "I WOULD STILL LAUGH."
 "I'D STILL BE JOYFUL"

01:21:33.600 --> 01:21:37.132
 "TO KNOW THAT EVERY BONE"
 "OF YOUR LIFE IS BROKEN;"

01:21:37.164 --> 01:21:41.000
 "YOU ARE LEFT HOPELESS,"
 "FRIENDLESS, MATELESS,"

01:21:41.032 --> 01:21:45.200
 "CHILDLESS, AVOIDED"
 "BY GODS AND MEN,"

01:21:45.232 --> 01:21:54.800
 "UNCLEAN WITH AWFUL"
 "EXCESS OF GRIEF - CHILDLESS."

01:21:54.832 --> 01:22:00.900
 "IT DOES NOT MATTER NOW"
 "WHO LIVES OR WHO DIES."

01:22:00.932 --> 01:22:03.932
 "GO DOWN TO YOUR SHIP"
 "ARGO AND WEEP BESIDE IT,"

01:22:03.964 --> 01:22:06.432
 "THAT ROTTING HULK ON"
 "THE HARBOR-BEACH"

01:22:06.464 --> 01:22:09.464
 "DRAWN DRY ASTRAND, NEVER"
 "TO BE LAUNCHED AGAIN"

01:22:09.500 --> 01:22:12.732
 "- EVEN THE WEEDS AND"
 "BARNACLES ON THE WARPED KEEL"

01:22:12.764 --> 01:22:18.900
 "ARE DEAD AND STINK - THAT'S YOUR"
 "LAST COMPANION, AND ONLY HOPE."

01:22:18.932 --> 01:22:25.864
 "FOR SOMETIME ONE OF THE ROTTING"
 "TIMBERS WILL FALL ON YOUR HEAD"

01:22:25.900 --> 01:22:31.264
 "AND KILL YOU: MEANWHILE"
 "SIT THERE AND MOURN,"

01:22:31.300 --> 01:22:34.232
 "REMEMBERING"
 "THE INFINITE EVIL,"

01:22:34.264 --> 01:22:37.600
 "AND THE GOOD"
 "THAT YOU MADE EVIL."

01:22:37.632 --> 01:22:45.200
 "GIVE ME MY BOYS: THE LITTLE"
 "PITIFUL VIOLATED BODIES:"

01:22:45.232 --> 01:22:48.764
 "THAT I MAY BURY THEM"
 "IN SOME KIND PLACE."

01:22:48.800 --> 01:22:51.732
 "TO YOU? YOU WOULD BETRAY"
 "EVEN THE LITTLE BODIES:"

01:22:51.764 --> 01:22:55.600
 "COIN THEM FOR SILVER,"
 "SELL THEM FOR POWER. NO."

01:22:55.632 --> 01:23:02.232
 "LET ME TOUCH THEIR DEAR FLESH,"
 "LET ME TOUCH THEIR HAIR!"

01:23:02.264 --> 01:23:05.132
 "NO, THEY ARE MINE."

01:23:05.164 --> 01:23:09.500
 "THEY ARE GOING WITH ME:"
 "THE CHARIOT IS AT THE GATE."

01:23:09.532 --> 01:23:14.432
 "YOU HAD LOVE"
 "AND BETRAYED IT;"

01:23:14.464 --> 01:23:20.200
 "NOW OF ALL MEN YOU ARE"
 "UTTERLY THE MOST MISERABLE."

01:23:20.232 --> 01:23:26.100
 "AS I OF WOMEN."

01:23:26.132 --> 01:23:31.232
 "BUT I, A WOMAN, A FOREIGNER,"
 "ALONE AGAINST YOU"

01:23:31.264 --> 01:23:36.400
 "AND THE MIGHT OF CORINTH,"
 "HAVE MET YOU THROAT FOR THROAT,"

01:23:36.432 --> 01:23:45.032
 "EVIL FOR EVIL,"
 "GRIEF FOR GRIEF."

01:23:53.164 --> 01:24:02.364
 "AND I GO FORTH UNDER THE"
 "COLD, CLEAR EYES OF HEAVEN;"

01:24:02.400 --> 01:24:13.332
 "THOSE WEAKNESS-DESPISING"
 "STARS: NOT ME THEY SCORN."